(4, '漓江、榕杉湖景区', '12层', '/attached/image/20120823/20120823144105_464.jpg', '桂林 秀峰区 杉湖北路1号', '桂林漓江大瀑布饭店 ★★★★★', '652', '2010-07-27 00:00:00', '<table style="font-size:12px;font-family:����;color:#21324E;" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" height="241" width="727">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="font-family:����;" align="center" height="127" width="239">\r\n				<img src="/attached/image/20120823/20120823144312_928.jpg" alt="" height="117" width="174" /><br />\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="font-family:����;" align="center" width="241">\r\n				<img src="/attached/image/20120823/20120823144410_499.jpg" alt="" height="118" width="161" /><br />\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="font-family:����;" align="center" width="247">\r\n				<img src="/attached/image/20120823/20120823144454_996.jpg" alt="" height="117" width="162" /><br />\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="font-family:����;" align="center" width="247">\r\n				<img src="/attached/image/20120823/20120823144533_691.jpg" alt="" height="120" width="156" /><br />\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="font-family:����;" align="center" height="33" valign="top">\r\n				<br />\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="font-family:����;" align="center">\r\n				<br />\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="font-family:����;" align="center">\r\n				<br />\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="font-family:����;" align="center">\r\n				<br />\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan="4" style="font-family:����;" height="84">\r\n				<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 桂林漓江大瀑布饭店规模大、设施设备豪华，它在原漓江饭店的基础上，以水景文化为背景，投资四个亿进行大规模的改扩建。饭店地处桂林市中心的繁华地段，东临秀丽的漓江，正对碧波荡漾的杉湖，南邻象山公园，北望独秀峰、叠彩山，环境怡人。<br />\r\n　　桂林漓江大瀑布饭店拥有上部宽72米、下部宽75米、落水高度达45米的大型人造瀑布，已列入大世界基尼斯纪录。</span> \r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan="4" style="font-family:����;">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<strong><strong>周边环境</strong>：</strong><span>象鼻山、漓江、伏波山、七星公园、榕湖景区、杉湖</span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<strong><strong>基本信息</strong>：</strong><span>1976年开业</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; <span>2010年装修</span>&nb