0000;">（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">60</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">分钟），游览“一代才人，名传万口”的明代解元，堪称“江南第一流才子”唐伯虎的园林</span><span style="color:#000000;">-----</span><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">苏州名园</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12pt;color:#000000;">[</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">唐寅园</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12pt;color:#000000;">]</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">60</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">分钟）</span><span style="color:black;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="bottom" width="72">\r\n				<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n					<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12px;">宿</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">苏州</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;color:red;"></span></b> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n					<b><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">（春申湖酒店或同级）</span></b><span style="color:red;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="67">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;">第四天</span><span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="598">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">赴杭州</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">小时）</span><b><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; </span></span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">参观红顶商人</span><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">胡雪岩故居</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">60</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">分钟）</span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;"> ：</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">感受清末中国巨商第一宅的雄浑大气</span><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; </span></span></span><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">船游西湖【休闲环湖游</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">】</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">45</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">分钟）</span><b><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">碧波之中感受西子风情</span><b><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">花港观鱼</span><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">晚可自选观赏“宋城千古情”</span><span style="color:#000000;"> [</span><span style="color:#000000;">参考价格为</span><span style="color:#000000;">240-280</span><span style="color:#000000;">元</span><span style="color:#000000;">/</span><span style="color:#000000;">人</span><span style="color:#000000;">] </span><span style="color:#000000;">或者“</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">吴越千古情</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">”</span><span style="color:#000000;"> [</span><span style="color:#000000;">参考价格为</span><span style="color:#000000;">200-240</span><span style="color:#000000;">元</span><span style="color:#000000;">/</span><span style="color:#000000;">人</span><span style="color:#000000;">]</span><span style="color:#000000;">精彩表演表演</span><span style="color:#000000;">(</span><span style="color:#000000;">约</span><span style="color:#000000;">2</span><span style="color:#000000;">小时</span><span><span style="color:#000000;">)</span><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">）</span><span style="color:black;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" align="center" valign="bottom" width="72">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<b><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">宿</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12px;">杭州</span></b><span style="color:red;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="67">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;">第五天</span><span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="598">\r\n				<p style="margin-left:.05pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">用早餐 </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#FF6600;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">欣赏丝绸时装表演 </span></b></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">100</span><span style="color:#000000;">分钟） </span></span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;">赴枕水江南</span><span style="color:#000000;">----</span></span><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">乌镇二期（西栅景区）</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">120</span><span style="color:#000000;">分钟 ） 游乌镇西栅景区（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">60</span><span style="color:#000000;">分钟）：参观草木本色染坊、昭明书院、乌镇老邮局、乌镇大戏院、漫步在石板路上，没有车辆喧闹，没有商家的吆喝，体味原住民生活韵味，一个感觉：静，透彻身心！</span><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color:#000000;">赴上海（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">1.4</span><span style="color:#000000;">小时）</span><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color:#000000;">晚上</span></span><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">[</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#FF6600;"><span style="color:#000000;">环球金融中心</span><span style="color:#000000;">94</span><span style="color:#000000;">层</span><span style="color:#000000;">]</span></span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">，一览新旧上海风貌。赴曾经的十里洋场，今天的中华第一街―――</span><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">[</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#FF6600;"><span style="color:#000000;">南京路步行街</span><span style="color:#000000;">]</span></span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">，感受灯光璀璨，感受流光异彩。</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="bottom" width="72">\r\n				<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n					<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">宿上海</span></b><span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="67">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;">第六天</span><span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="598">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">早餐后</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;"><span style="color:#000000;">重温精彩世博：游览上海世博</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">【</span></b><b><span style="color:#FF6600;"><span style="color:#000000;">沙特馆</span><span style="color:#000000;">】</span></span></b><span style="color:#000000;">（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">100</span><span style="color:#000000;">分钟）</span><span style="color:#000000;">[</span><span style="color:red;"><span style="color:#000000;">周一闭馆</span><span style="color:#000000;">]</span></span><span style="color:#000000;">游览</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">［</span></b><b><span style="color:#000000;">能源之城、绿之城、文化古城、新经济之城</span><span style="color:#000000;">］</span></b><span style="color:#000000;">感受独特魅力</span></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; </span></span><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;">乘坐都市观光车</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;"><span style="color:#000000;">：畅游大上海，途经上海各著名景点</span><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color:#000000;">行程参考 </span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">：</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">浦东新区</span><b><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;">感受浦东新区开发开放日新月异</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">。</span><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">外滩</span> </b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;">欣赏美仑美换的“万国建筑博览群”</span><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color:#000000;">漫步“中华商业街”的</span></span><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#000000;">[</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#FF6600;"><span style="color:#000000;">南京路步行街</span><span style="color:#000000;">]</span></span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;"><span style="color:#000000;">（注：当日</span><span style="color:#000000;">17</span><span style="color:#000000;">点以后陆续送团）乘晚班机</span><span style="color:#000000;"> 9C8805</span><span style="color:#000000;">航班</span><span style="color:#000000;">20</span><span style="color:#000000;">：</span><span style="color:#000000;">30</span><span style="color:#000000;">上海浦东飞桂林</span></span><span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="bottom" width="72">\r\n				<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n					<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">送</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">团</span><span></span></b> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="67">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:7.5pt;font-family:宋体;">接送安排</span><span style="font-size:7.5pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="670">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">我社导游举黄底绿字<b><i>“春之旅”</i></b>导游旗恭迎各地贵宾</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">上海火车站西南出口处、（接） 上海：浦东机场<span><span>&nbsp; </span></span>虹桥机场出口处<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>（送） 上海浦东机场<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;</span></span>虹桥机场</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="67">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:7.5pt;font-family:宋体;">特别提示</span><span style="font-size:7.5pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="670">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">持老年证、军官证者景点门票已含在旅游团费中，不予退还门票差价！</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:幼圆;"></span></b> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="67">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:7.5pt;font-family:宋体;">住宿安排</span><span style="font-size:7.5pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="670">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:幼圆;">第四晚苏州赠送五星同级住宿，其余</span></b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">为<b><i><u>挂牌四星级</u></i></b>宾馆双人标房<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">如行程内单人须补<b>房差</b>四星：<span>880</span>元（五晚） </span><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span>&nbsp;</span><span style="color:red;">延住<span>500</span>元<span>/</span>间<span>/</span>天（</span></span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;">（导游协助，客人自行赴机场。）</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;">）</span></b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:华文中宋;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="67">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:7.5pt;font-family:宋体;">旅游用车</span><span style="font-size:7.5pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="670">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">空调旅游车（每人一个正座）</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">旅游过程中所用的车辆，十人成团，以实际接待人数为准核定车型</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="67">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:7.5pt;font-family:宋体;">景点门票</span><span style="font-size:7.5pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="670">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">各景点第一大门票</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">,</span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="67">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:7.5pt;font-family:宋体;">用餐安排</span><span style="font-size:7.5pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="670">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;">5</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">早</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">7</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">正餐</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">,</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">宾馆内提供<span>[</span>早餐自助早<span>]</span>，正餐每人<span>25</span>元<span>/</span>餐标<span>;</span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">杭州其中一正餐为风味菜馆“山外山”用餐，餐标</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">60</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">元</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">/</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">人</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;"></span></b> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="67">\r\n				<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:7.5pt;font-family:黑体;">导游服务<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="670">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">地陪中文导游讲解服务</span><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;"></span></b> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="67">\r\n				<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:7.5pt;font-family:黑体;">儿童标准<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="670">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">1.2</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">米</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">以下儿童收<b><span>480</span></b>元<span>/</span>人（占车位、不占床位、产生门票自理、含半餐）<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">1.2</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">米</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">以上儿童按大人标准收费、享受大人待遇、如不占床则扣除相应的床位费</span><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;"></span></b> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="67">\r\n				<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:7.5pt;font-family:黑体;">购物安排<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="670">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">欣赏丝绸时装表演（约</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">100</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">分钟）</span><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;"></span></b> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="67">\r\n				<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:7.5pt;font-family:黑体;">自选项目及名称<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="670">\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>1.<span> </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">杭</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">州</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">晚可自选观赏“宋城千古情”<span> [</span>参考价格为<span>240-280</span>元<span>/</span>人<span>] </span>或者“</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">吴越千古情</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">”<span> [</span>参考价格为<span>200-240</span>元<span>/</span>人<span>]</span>精彩表演<span>(</span>约<span>2</span>小时<span>)</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>2.<span> </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">上海夜景含外滩夜景</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">,</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">浦江游船</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">,</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">登东方明珠</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">263M</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">观光厅或环球金融中心</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">94</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">层</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">)</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">［参考价格</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">220</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">元起</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">/</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">人］</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;"><span>3.</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">全程自由活动</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">2</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">次（如上海不</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">游不住自由活动</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">1</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">次）时间视情况而定</span><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;"></span></b> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="67">\r\n				<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:7.5pt;font-family:黑体;">备注<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="670">\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>1.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">如持军官证，记者证等可减免门票的有效证件，门票按旅行社折扣价退还</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>2.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">如遇国家政策性调整门票、交通价格等，则按实际价格结算。</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>3.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">因人力不可抗因素造成的游览变化和景点减少、本社只负责退还门票差额、不承担由此造成的损失和责任</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>4.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">如上团后临时放弃当地景点、用餐、住宿等，其费用本社均不退还</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>5.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">根据世博局规定沙特馆按当日票面售价享七五折优惠：</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">60</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">岁以上老人；现役军人；残疾人士；中，小学生（不包括大学生）；身高超</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">1.3</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">米</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">儿童，一个成人可携带一个</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">1.3</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">米</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">以下儿童。以上人群一律凭相关有效证件到我社导游现退差价。</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="67">\r\n				<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:7.5pt;font-family:黑体;">游客须知<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="670">\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>1.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">出门前请带好有效证件（如身份证等），并告知家人出游计划，保持通讯畅通，以便随时联系。</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>2.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">华东地区早晚气温比较低，请游客准备好衣物防止着凉，携带雨具，以防天气变化。</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>3.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">华东地区的饮食口味以清淡为主，建议游客可以根据自己的饮食习惯，提前跟导游讲明以便跟酒店安排。同时，在旅游过程中，注意饮食卫生，以防吃坏身体，带来不便。</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>4.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">游客在旅游过程中应尊重旅游地的风土人情和民族习俗，维护环境卫生，遵守公共秩序，保护生态环境和文物古迹，尊重他人，以礼待人。</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>5.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">游客应遵守团队纪律、配合领队、导游工作。因自身疾病等原因不能随团前行，需书面申请并经领队、导游签字同意，如未经书面同意而擅自离团，所造成的人身和财产损失，旅行社概不承担责任。旅游行程外出游请结伴同行。</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>6.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">未成年人参加旅游活动，须事先征得旅行社同意，并由法定监护人陪同出游。监护人负责未成年人在旅游过程中的安全问题。</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>7.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">中老年人尤其是患病者参加旅游，须如实向旅行社提供健康信息，并根据自己的健康状况量力而行。如游客感觉身体不适，请马上告知导游。因中老年游客身体原因产生的一切后果与责任，旅行社概不承担。</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n					<span style="font-size:9.0pt;"><span>8.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">各地宾馆设施均有差异，如浴室内无防滑垫，洗澡时请特别注意安全，防止滑倒</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">;</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">老人冬季洗澡时间不宜过长</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">.</span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />', 3090, '桂林', 4, '飞机/大巴', 1, 7, 14, 1, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('OverseasTour', 30, 3180, 3880, '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">★交通：皇岗口岸集合，皇巴过关；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">★景点：香港全景游览：星光大道、海洋公园、会展中心/金紫荆广场、迪士尼乐园； </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体;color:black;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体;color:black;"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">澳门全景游览：威尼斯人度假村、妈祖庙、大三巴、渔人码头、金莲花广场；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">★特别加游：乘坐大型游船游览维多利亚海港夜景；</span><b><span style="font-family:黑体;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">★</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">用餐</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">：</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">正餐不低于</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">$30</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">元</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">/</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">人</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">；</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">早餐不低于</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">$20</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">元</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">/</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">人</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">；<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">★导游：专业深圳领队及香港澳门导游随团服务，全程无强制购物，澳门走一站手信，真正品质游；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">★特别安排一天时间自由活动，您可以自游自在感受东方之珠的魅力；</span><b><span style="font-family:黑体;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">★服务完整，安心保障；澳门时间游览充裕。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">报价包含：</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">1、景点：行程表内所列的景点第一道门票； </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">2、交通：皇巴、旅游巴士、过澳船票；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">3、用餐：4正3早；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">4、专业深圳领队及香港澳门导游随团服务；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">5、旅行社责任险；旅游签注（L签注）产生的口岸服务费：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">6、深圳一晚准三标准酒店，香港三星酒店3晚、澳门三星酒店1晚。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:10.8pt;text-indent:-10.5pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">7、桂林/深圳往返机票或广州/桂林机票。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">费用不含</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">1、行程外私人所产生的个人费用； </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">2、香港导游及司机小费：全程￥200元/人；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">3、旅游意外险30元/人；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">4、机建燃油费220元/人</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:11.1pt;text-indent:-47.55pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5、周五、六香港、澳门房差50元/人.</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:11.1pt;text-indent:-47.55pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#D9D9D9;"><span><span></span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 备注：21岁以下和55岁以上客人价格另议，客人必需自备身份证（小孩带上户口本），</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">赠送30万元旅游意外险。（被保人条件年龄在小孩满2-70周岁之间的）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '11月30日前', '/attached/image/20120815/20120815154038_858.jpg', '桂林双飞港澳（海+迪）优质纯玩六日', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">D1:</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;">自行前往机场，乘机前往深圳，</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:black;">深圳接机送酒店。住深圳</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span><span style="font-family:黑体;color:black;font-size:16px;">D2</span><span style="font-size:16px;">:</span></span>早上7:00酒店接起，送皇岗口岸三楼出境厅正门集合，约8：15在导游的带领下乘坐皇岗穿梭巴士前往香港落马洲，随后换乘旅游大巴前往香港。首先前往尖沙咀落成在海滨长廊上的</span><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;">“星光大道”（约20分钟）</span></u></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">，</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">之后参观香港旅发局“优质旅游服务”认证的</span><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;">环球国际免税店DFS（约1小时）</span></u></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:black;"></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">。然后前往尖沙咀餐厅享用午餐。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">午餐后前往著名的</span><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;">香港海洋公园（约3小时）</span></u></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">，游毕前往香港市区酒楼用餐。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">晚上</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">乘车前往游览</span><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;">香港会展中心新翼、金紫荆广场（约20分钟）</span></u></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">，这里是香港回归祖国的见证，</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;">“</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">永远盛开的紫荆花</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;">”</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">面朝维多利亚海港，寓意着香港永远繁荣昌盛</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">。然后乘坐大型观光船：</span><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;">游览著名维多利亚海港夜景（约45分钟）</span></u></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">。游毕后，乘车送返酒店。</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:black;"> 住香港</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:16px;">D3：</span>早餐后乘车前往</span><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;">香港迪士尼乐园（全天）</span></u></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">：在那里可走进园内四个主题景区：【美国小镇】、【幻想世界】、【探险世界】、【明日世界】，任意穿梭时空，融入童话世界之中。更有最新园区【反斗奇兵大本营】火爆开放。于导游<b>约定时间集合</b>，乘车返回酒店（一般为下午4点-5点，如游客要观看烟花汇演或另有安排，则自理交通）。 住香港<br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:16px;">D4：</span>全天自由活动，可去铜锣湾、尖沙咀或旺角等香港著名的商业区，充分感受香港购物的魅力。 住香港</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;"> </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">D5:早餐后乘船前往澳门，抵达后首先前往亚洲最大的综合性娱乐场所：</span><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;">威尼斯人度假村（约1小时）</span></u></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">。之后用午餐。餐后前往</span><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;">澳门手信店自由购物（约1小时）</span></u></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">，</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">游客可购买特产赠送亲友。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">随后游览澳门各大名胜<b>：</b>被列入世界遗产名录的</span><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;">妈祖阁（约20分钟）、</span></u></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">澳门最具代表性的名胜古迹、圣保罗大教堂前壁</span><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;">大三巴牌坊（约20分钟）、</span></u></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">由博彩巨头何鸿燊和知名商人周锦辉联手兴建的澳门第一个主题公园<b><u><span style="color:blue;">渔人码头（约30分钟）、</span></u></b></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">象征澳门永远繁荣昌盛的“盛世莲花”座落地</span><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;">金莲花广场（约15分钟）。</span></u></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">途中可看到<b>友谊大桥、澳门观光塔、望海观音像</b>等。晚餐后送返酒店（游客也可自费观赏澳门特色表演项目，体验澳门精彩夜生活） 住澳门</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">D6:早餐后酒店大堂集合（具体时间由导游约定），在导游的带领下前往拱北口岸，过关，后乘大巴返回深圳机场或广州机场，乘机返回桂林。结束愉快旅程！</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 3680, '桂林', 8, '飞机', 11, 7, 1, 4, 2, 1, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tour` (`dtype`, `id`, `children`, `door_price`, `feature`, `group_date`, `image`, `name`, `plan`, `privilege`, `start_city`, `version`, `way`, `address`, `tour_day`, `type`, `sort`, `recommend`, `city_id`, `description`, `keywords`) VALUES
('OverseasTour', 31, 2180, 2880, '<span style="background-color:initial;"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<table align="left" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" valign="top">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">行程特点：<span></span></span></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">1、</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">游览景点：黄大仙/ 星光大道/会展中心/金紫荆广场/海洋公园</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">维港夜游</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">/大三巴牌坊/迪士尼/妈祖阁/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">盛世莲花</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">/威尼斯人度假村</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span>2、<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">港段：深圳领队及香港导游陪同讲解；澳段：\r\n  澳门导游陪同讲解服务；</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span>3、<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">全程不进指定购物点，绝无强制购物，香港段无自费项目，澳门段保证绝无强迫的前提挑选特色项目供参考。</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<table align="left" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" valign="top">\r\n					<br />\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</div>', '11月30日前', '/attached/image/20120816/20120816110333_482.jpg', '桂林双飞港澳纯玩6日游', '<p>\r\n	D1：<b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">桂林乘机飞深圳，深圳机场接机，送客人到酒店休息。</span></b> 住深圳\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	D2：<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">早上7：30在酒店接起送皇岗口岸3楼出境大厅集合，然后在领队带领下搭乘旅游巴士前往香港，游览香火最旺的庙宇-<b><u>-黄大仙（约30分钟）</u></b>，</span><span style="font-family:楷体;color:black;">之后游览香港</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">尖沙咀海滨长廊上的<b><u>星光大道（约20分钟）</u></b>此长廊全长440公尺，展现了香港电影百年发展历史，有电影里程碑及舞台连屏幕,还有沿途设置的香港电影名人手印和牌匾。中<b>餐</b></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">后</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">赴香港港岛参观香港<b><u>会展中心新翼和金紫荆广场（约20分钟）</u></b>，这里为香港回归祖国的见证，团友可于“永远盛开的紫荆花”及回归的纪念碑旁拍照留念。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">后前往闻名世界的<b><u>海洋公园（约3小时）</u>，</b>这里有世界最大的水族馆、鲨鱼馆及海洋剧场，有海豚、海狮、杀人鲸等精彩特技表演；还有各式各样惊险刺激的机动游乐设施，如过山车、摩天轮、海盗船等。游毕乘亚洲最长的户外登山电梯下行参观集古村--置身其中，仿佛走进时光隧道，重温中国过去十三个朝代历史，场内有艺术品及工艺品制作示范、街头表演等。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">餐后在九龙城码头乘<b><u>观光船游览维多利亚港（约45分钟），</u></b>观光船沿着九龙半岛及港岛北面海岸畅游维多利亚港观赏香港华丽的夜景。自由参观<b>DFS国际免税店（约45分钟）</b>，游毕乘车返回</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">酒店休息。 住香港</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">D3：约定时间用<b>早餐</b>，</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">前往<b><u> 免税中心</u></b>自由购物<b>（约2小时）</b>在此可选择到世界品牌电器等各类香港代表产品，</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"> </span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">到达<b><u>香港</u></b></span><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">迪士尼乐园（指定时间集合）</span></u></b><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"> ：</span></u></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">走过睡公主城堡，来到充满二十世纪初的美国风情的美国小镇大街，您便会不其然地放缓步伐，享受一下阵阵烘饼及糖果的香味，欣赏两旁雅朴怀旧的建筑物。在妙想天开的幻想世界中，那迷人的故事和永恒的国度，都生动地展现在您的眼前。还可到探险世界里寻幽探秘，在明日世界内探索宇宙的无穷奥秘。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">任意穿梭时空，融入童话世界之中，充分感受迪士尼乐园带给你的欢乐，重温童时的梦想，于指定时间<b><u> </u></b>集合送回酒店休息，如在约定时间外的回程由客人自理。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"> 住香港</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">D4：<b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">香港</span></b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">全天自由活动。（</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">不含餐/车/导游</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">）</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">D5：<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">早餐由香港导游带领于中港城码头餐厅用餐后乘船前往澳门（一般乘坐早上7：30分的船班，</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">酒店集合须提前两小时</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">）。</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">到达</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">后由澳门导游带领游览澳门各大名胜，</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">延途可乘车可观到望海觀音,游覽澳門回歸紀念廣場<b><u>金蓮花廣場（约10分钟）</u></b>,有標志性的建筑物<b><u>圣保罗教堂遗迹大三巴牌坊、可自行登上大炮台</u></b><u>（<b>约20分钟），</b></u>后到澳门的起源及最古老的庙宇<b><u>妈祖阁（约20分钟）、</u></b>在车上可远观到主教山，游毕后到<b><u>澳门手信店约</u></b><u>（<b>60分钟）</b></u>购买代表性的澳门特产肉干、杏仁饼、老婆饼等食品。午餐后至澳融合世界各地不同和建筑風格及中西文化特色的<b>[<u>漁人碼頭]及[巴比倫娱乐城]（约60分钟）</u>。</b>后到亚州最大的娱乐城<b><u>威尼斯人度假村观光游览（约1.5小时）</u></b>。游完后晚餐。晚餐后可自愿参加澳门特色表演项目（RMB450元/人），体验澳门夜生活，或直接<span>送回酒店休息。</span></span> 住澳门</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">D6：<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">于珠海送回程含：珠海车游情侣路，渔女像，九洲城外景，配合进百货店（约45分钟店）、珠宝（约45分钟店），送深圳机场或广州机场，乘飞机返桂林结束愉快行程！</span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:20.6pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 2580, '桂林', 9, '双飞', 1, 7, 1, 3, 2, 1, NULL, NULL),
('OverseasTour', 32, 7080, 7580, '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">品质推荐：<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">全程无自费<span>,</span>境外轻松旅游<span>, </span>全程<span>4-5</span>星酒店<span>, </span>入住<span>1</span>晚豪华温泉<span>,</span>赠送市场上自费，贈送市場上自費总值超过<span>RMB3300</span>元！更增量赠送台场小火车<span>!!! </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">(</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">精明客户<span>: </span>比较市场上差价<span>,</span>注意行程酒店入住透明度及用餐内容<span>,</span>本社不打擦边球<span>,</span>表面化文字容易影响明智决择<span>!)</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">特色美食：</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">★</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">温泉酒店料理</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">★</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日式烤肉<span>BBQ</span>自助餐<span>★</span>天妇罗定食<span>★</span>京都汤豆腐料理<span>★</span>各式定食<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:Wingdings;"><span>à</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">全程已包含<span>5</span>顿特色正餐<span>, </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">绝非一般低价团仅吃中餐或便当定食可媲美！<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">&lt;&lt;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">精明的您又岂能错过！<span>&gt;&gt;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:19.85pt;text-align:left;text-indent:-14.2pt;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:blue;"><span>u<span> </span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">特别赠送金阁寺<span>+</span>祉园艺妓街\r\n–价值日元<span>6,500/</span>人<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:19.85pt;text-align:left;text-indent:-14.2pt;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:blue;"><span>u<span> </span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">特别赠送富士山五合目<span>+ </span>山中湖花之都公园–价值日元<span>6,500/</span>人<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:19.85pt;text-align:left;text-indent:-14.2pt;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:blue;"><span>u<span> </span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">特别赠送横滨观光<span> : </span>中华街<span>+</span>山下公园<span>+21</span>世纪未来港<span>+</span>横滨港湾–价值日元<span>7,500/</span>人<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:19.85pt;text-align:left;text-indent:-14.2pt;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:blue;"><span>u<span> </span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">特别赠送<span>LALAPORT</span>购物中心–价值日元<span>4,000/</span>人<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:19.85pt;text-align:left;text-indent:-14.2pt;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:blue;"><span>u<span> </span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">特别赠送银座购物乐<span>+</span>表参道<span>HILLS</span>自由购物<span>+</span>烧烤自助餐–价值日元<span>9,500/</span>人<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;">特别赠送新宿歌舞妓町<span>+</span>天妇罗定食–价值日元<span>7,000/</span>成人</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">费用包含：</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、广西<span>-</span>广州<span>-</span>大阪、东京<span>-</span>广州<span>-</span>广西机票及燃油附加税费；<span>2</span>、酒店：全程<span>4-5</span>星级酒店双人间（温泉酒店除外）温泉酒店保证<span>2</span>人一间；<span>3</span>、用餐：行程中所列用餐食（<span>5</span>早<span>5</span>正）； </span><span style="font-family:宋体;">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、保险：旅行社责任险、旅游意外险等；<span>4</span>、导游：中日双语领队兼翻译、旅游当地中文专职导游<span style="color:black;">；</span><span>5</span>、用车：境外空调旅游车；<span>6</span>、门票：行程所列观光景点门票；<span>7</span>、签证：团队旅游签证费用。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">费用不含：<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:17.35pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;"><span>1、<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">护照费；<span>2</span>、个人消费及小费（日本：人民币<span>50</span>元<span>/</span>人<span>/</span>天按<span>6</span>天计<span>=300</span>元<span>/</span>人）；<span>3</span>、自由活动时产生的一切费用（不含车、餐、导游）；<span>4</span>、单间差<span>450</span>元<span>/</span>晚<span>/</span>间。<span>5</span>、机票燃油附加费的临时涨幅。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '此线路暂时取消', '/attached/image/20120816/20120816105345_239.jpg', '日本暑假舒心欢乐6日游', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:-.65pt;text-indent:10.5pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">D1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">：广西各地集合，乘航班前往广州白云国际机场，酒店巴士免费班车接机<span>,</span>入住机场酒店休息。住广州<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:-.65pt;text-indent:10.5pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">D2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">：早餐后，乘坐免费班车到机场乘国际航班（<span>CZ389 08:30-13:00</span>）飞往日本大阪，酒店巴士免费班车接机<span>,</span>入住机场酒店休息。下午自由活动！\r\n住关西机场附近<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:-.65pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">&nbsp; D3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">：酒店早餐后前往，【<b>大阪城公园</b>】日本三大城堡之一「大阪城」，后游览百货商店与各式专门店等为大阪代表性的中心商务区【<b>心斋桥</b>】。乘车前往京都游览【<b>平安神宫</b>】及【<b>西阵织和服会馆</b>】。之后前往<b>【赠送金阁寺（约<span>50</span>分钟）<span>+</span>祉园艺妓街街（约<span>45</span>分钟） –价值日元<span>6,500/</span>人】</b></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">【金阁寺】</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">，<b>【祗园艺伎街</b></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">】</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">电影艺伎回忆录中出现的场景─【祗园花见小路】，是祗园街正中南北走向的一条保持了京都历史古老风貌的著名街道。有机会的时候，间或可见外出献艺的艺伎的挑帘进出、小步急行的窈窕身影，增添古都风情。\r\n住中部地区<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:10.5pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">D4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">：酒店早餐后，前往富士山风景区，【<b>河口湖畔</b>】河口湖，富士五湖之一，后游览【<b>平和日式庭园</b>】及【<b>舍利白塔</b>】圣白的佛塔里供奉着释迦牟尼佛的舍利子，充满灵秀与肃穆气氛。<b>【赠<span style="color:black;">送富士山五合目（约<span>60</span>分钟）<span>+ </span>山中湖花之都公园欣赏季节花海（约<span>60</span>分钟）–价值日元<span>6,500/</span>人<span>(</span>视乎天气情况及季节而</span>定<span>) </span>】住富士山地区<span></span></b></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:10.5pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">D5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">：酒店早餐后，乘车前往横滨地区，游览<span>【</span><b>赠送横滨观光<span> : </span>中华街<span>+</span>山下公园<span>+21</span>世纪未来港<span>+</span>横滨港湾</b>–价值日元<span>8,000/</span>人</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">】，</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">后前往东京游览【<b>皇居外苑</b></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">‧</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">二重桥</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">】</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。继而前往日本人气产品免税专门店<span>, </span>客人可自由选购各种日本国民之健康流行食品及各种日本手信【<b>光伸或大亚或<span>JTC</span>免税店</b>】</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，游览</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">【</span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">赠送银座购物乐<span> +</span>表参道<span>HILLS</span>自由购物<span>+</span>烧烤自助餐</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">–价值日元<span>9,500/</span>人</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">】</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、<span>【</span><b>赠送新宿歌舞伎町<span>+</span>天妇罗定食<span>(</span>行程第<span>2</span>晚安排<span>)</span></b><span> </span>–价值日元<span>7,000/</span>人</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">】。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">【<b>横滨中华街（约<span>45</span>分钟）</b>】<span>横滨</span>开港以来建成的<strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:normal;">横滨中华街</span></strong>至今已有<span>140</span>余年历史。是日本最大的<span>唐人街</span>。【<b>山下公园（约<span>30</span>分钟）</b>】是日本最早的临海公园。【<b><span>21</span>世纪未来港（约<span>40</span>分钟）</b>】超世纪亮丽、绚烂的复合城市，简称『<span>MM21</span>』。日本填海造陆开发城市最成功的典范。【<b>银座（约<span>60</span>分钟）</b>】、【<b>表参道<span>HILLS</span>（约<span>45</span>分钟）</b>】表、【<b>新宿歌舞伎町（约<span>30</span>分钟）</b>】是日本著名的欢乐街。住东京<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:10.5pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">D6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">：</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">酒店早餐后，前往【<b>浅草雷门观音寺</b>】及【<b>仲见世商店街</b>】浅草寺前的购物小街，游客可在此选购特色手信。远眺东京塔“天空树<span>Sky Tree”</span>游览<span>【</span><b>赠送<span>LALAPORT</span>购物中心</b>–价值日元<span>4,000/</span>人</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">】</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">LaLaport</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大型购物商场包括了各种娱乐设施。继而前往【<b>永山或<span>TOKIS</span>或<span>LAOX</span>电气店</b>】日本最新款、最高科技电器及电子产品【</span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">台场海滨公园</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">】<span>(</span>眺望东京湾彩虹桥及富士电视台美景<span>)</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，<b><span style="color:blue;">自选畅游<span>:</span></span><span> </span></b>东京迪斯尼乐园<span>(</span>门票自理–日元<span>6,200/</span>成人、<span>12</span>岁以下小童日元<span>4,100-10</span>人成行<span>)</span>（约<span>3-4</span>小时）。【<b>台场海滨公园（约<span>40</span>分钟）】</b></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">彩虹大桥是台场最醒目的地标，也是日本偶像剧的取景圣地，这座桥横跨东京湾，连接芝浦及台场。台场海滨公园<span>, </span>是一处人工沙滩<span>, </span>是许多情侣的约会热点。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">【<b>台场小火车<span>(</span>约<span>15</span>分锺<span>) </span>】</b></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">又名无人驾驶列车<span>(Yurikamome),</span>坐这小火车能你深深体会现代科技\r\n住成田机场<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:10.5pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">D7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">：</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">酒店早餐后，乘酒店免费班车前往机场搭乘国际航班（<span>CZ386 15:30-19:30</span>）返回广州，再转乘国内航班返回广西，我们温暖的家，结束愉快的行程。</span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;"></span></b> \r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;"> </span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;"></span></b> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;"><span></span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span><span style="font-family:PMingLiU;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:PMingLiU;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span><span style="font-family:PMingLiU;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;"><span></span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span><span style="font-family:PMingLiU;"></span> \r\n</p>', 7280, '桂林', 10, '双飞', 1, 7, 2, 2, 2, 4, NULL, NULL),
('OverseasTour', 33, 4199, 4699, '<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="color:#365F91;">◤超值奉送◢：</span></b> <span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>1.</span>舒适旅程：韩亚航空豪华客机桂林直飞（<span>2011</span>年全球服务最佳航空）； <span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>2.</span>经典美食：人参鸡、济州烤黑猪肉无限量、帆船餐厅自助餐、猪排炖土豆火锅（李明博总统亲临过） <span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>3.</span>玩转首尔，济州：朝安泰迪熊博物馆、城山日出峰、华克山庄… <span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>4.</span>生活体验<span>- </span>济州海产品批发市场。 <span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>5.</span>引领时尚：韩国最大服装批发市场东大门都塔大厦自由购物<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>6.</span>贴心服务：专业韩语中文双语领队全程服务<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>7.</span>全程无自费，行程乐逍遥<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>8</span>．特别安排 韩国迪斯尼<span>-</span>爱宝乐园。 <span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:13.55pt;">\r\n	<span>&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:13.55pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">费用包含：</span></b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">国际往返机票及税（<span>4</span>程）、<span>3</span>早<span>8</span>正，飞机上用餐为正餐，韩国四花酒店（相当于国内<span>3</span>星）、行程中所列膳食、餐标（<span>5000</span>韩币、顿），境外旅游用车、景点第一门票、韩国中文导游服务、韩国团体签证、全程领队服务。</span> <span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">&nbsp;&nbsp; 费用未含：</span></b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">护照工本费，机场税（</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;">90</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">元），通关费（</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;">100</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">元），境外旅游意外险（</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;">30</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">元</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;">/</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">人），境外导游司机小费（</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;">5</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">天，</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;">250</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">元</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;">/</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">人）及个人消费</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;">,</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">单房差（</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;">1000</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">元），燃油税临时涨幅。</span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span><span><a href="http://www.guilincits.com/jingdian/yaoshan_18.html"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span></a></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span></span><span></span></span><span><a href="http://www.guilincits.com/jingdian/jingjiangwangcheng_21.html"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span></a></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span><span><a href="http://www.guilincits.com/jingdian/yijingsihu_146.html"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span></a></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span></span><span></span></span><span><a href="http://www.guilincits.com/jingdian/xiangshan_11.html"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span></a></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:13.55pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span></b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<pre></pre>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span></span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span></span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span></span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span>', '11月18、25日', '/attached/image/20120816/20120816145103_808.jpg', '畅游首尔浪漫济州5日游', '<span></span> \r\n<p style="text-indent:10.5pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:14px;">D1</span><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;"><span style="font-size:14px;">：</span><span><span style="font-size:14px;">指定时间在桂林两江国际机场集合。乘豪华客机赴韩国，开始愉快的旅程<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;">（</span><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;">23</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;">：<span>35/04</span>：<span>01</span>）</span></b>（桂林直航首尔的航班仅此一班，虽有些晚，但是相信美丽的韩国会让您有克服这点小困难的信心！祝您在飞机上有一个美丽的梦）。<span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;"><span><span style="color:red;font-size:14px;"></span></span><b><span style="color:red;"><span style="font-size:14px;"></span></span></b></span></span><span style="color:red;font-size:14px;"></span></span><b><span style="color:red;"><span style="font-size:14px;"></span></span><span></span></b></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:10.5pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:14px;">D2</span><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;"><span style="font-size:14px;">：抵达后，前往【汗蒸沐休息到</span><span style="font-size:14px;">11</span><span style="font-size:14px;">：</span><span style="font-size:14px;">00</span><span style="font-size:14px;">钟】</span><span style="font-size:14px;">(</span><span style="font-size:14px;">赠送</span><span style="font-size:14px;">)</span><span style="font-size:14px;">休息到</span><span style="font-size:14px;">11</span><span style="font-size:14px;">点钟：汗蒸窑与热疗室，作为美容观光的先头兵，只在韩国才有的独特体验，吸引了众多的游客。午餐后，乘车到首尔（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">50</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟），【首尔数码科技城】（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">90</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）（</span><span style="font-size:14px;">2</span><span style="font-size:14px;">楼，</span><span style="font-size:14px;">3</span><span style="font-size:14px;">楼利用高科技电脑免费体检后屏幕上医院专家马上解读结果并现场解读怎样养身。【战争纪念广场】（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">40</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）</span><span style="font-size:14px;">-B-52</span><span style="font-size:14px;">轰炸机</span><span style="font-size:14px;">/</span><span style="font-size:14px;">坦克</span><span style="font-size:14px;">/</span><span style="font-size:14px;">潜水艇等，晚餐后，前往金浦机场，乘机到韩国第一大岛—济州岛（称之为亚洲的夏威夷）。</span><span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:10.5pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:14px;">D3</span><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:14px;">：</span><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;"><span style="font-size:14px;">早餐后 【城山日出峰】（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">90</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）城山日出峰海拔</span><span style="font-size:14px;">182</span><span style="font-size:14px;">米，系</span><span style="font-size:14px;">10</span><span style="font-size:14px;">万年前海底火山爆发而形成。城山日出峰顶观日出可谓是叹为观止。【城邑民俗村】（</span><span style="font-size:14px;">40</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）位于汉拿山麓，是完全保存了韩国传统的一处民俗村。【涉地可支】（</span><span style="font-size:14px;">50</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）涉地可支</span><span style="font-size:14px;">(Sopjikogi)</span><span style="font-size:14px;">位于济州岛东部海岸的一端。涉地可支就是韩剧《洛城生死恋》的外景地。而《我叫金三顺》中，柳熙珍和她的帅哥男友去济州岛玩也曾经到了这里。【朝安泰迪熊博物馆】（</span><span style="font-size:14px;">50</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）位于济州岛南部西归浦市的中文观光旅游区内的</span><span style="font-size:14px;">Joanne Bear</span><span style="font-size:14px;">博物馆是世界上著名的泰迪熊设计师</span><span style="font-size:14px;">Joanne Oh</span><span style="font-size:14px;">的工作室展示空间。【龙头岩】（</span><span style="font-size:14px;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）由于岩石一端颇似龙头，故得名龙头岩。【生活体验】（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）济州最大的海产品批发市场。</span><span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:10.5pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:14px;">D4</span><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;"><span style="font-size:14px;">：早餐后，乘飞机飞往首尔金浦机场，抵达后游览韩国先朝的皇宫、首尔最大、最古老，具有</span><span style="font-size:14px;">500</span><span style="font-size:14px;">年历史—【景福宫】（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">60</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟），【国立民俗博物馆 】（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">40</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟），外观韩国当政的总统官邸</span><span style="font-size:14px;">-</span><span style="font-size:14px;">【青瓦台】（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">20</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟），参观高丽人参公卖局（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟），韩国化妆品免税店（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">60</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟），【泡菜学校】（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">30-40</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）学习韩国传统泡菜的制作方法，免费穿韩服拍照。【护肝宝保健中心】（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）以及，晚上参观韩剧主要室内拍摄地之一</span></span><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;"><span style="font-size:14px;">的【华克山庄】含世界名品集中的免税店（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">90</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟），后回酒店休息。</span><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; </span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:10.5pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:14px;">D5</span><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;"><span style="font-size:14px;">：早餐后，【南山韩屋村】（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">50</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）皇帝女儿居住过的地方也是大长今外景拍摄地之一。【清溪川市政工程】（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）也是首尔写字楼最集中的地方之一，【东大门都塔大厦 】（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">60</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）韩国时尚服装、皮衣，工艺品等最大批发市场自由购物，前往</span><span style="font-size:14px;">[</span><span style="font-size:14px;">南北韩军事分界线</span><span style="font-size:14px;">38</span><span style="font-size:14px;">线</span><span style="font-size:14px;">]</span><span style="font-size:14px;">之</span><span style="font-size:14px;">[</span><span style="font-size:14px;">临津阁</span><span style="font-size:14px;">]</span><span style="font-size:14px;">、</span><span style="font-size:14px;">[</span><span style="font-size:14px;">自由桥</span><span style="font-size:14px;">] [</span><span style="font-size:14px;">熬头山统一展望台</span><span style="font-size:14px;">+</span><span style="font-size:14px;">北朝鲜博物馆</span><span style="font-size:14px;">]</span><span style="font-size:14px;">（共</span><span style="font-size:14px;">4</span><span style="font-size:14px;">项</span><span style="font-size:14px;">200</span><span style="font-size:14px;">元</span><span style="font-size:14px;">/</span><span style="font-size:14px;">人），【土产店</span><span style="font-size:14px;">-</span><span style="font-size:14px;">】（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）为家人选购韩国特产海苔，海带，泡菜等礼品】</span><span style="font-size:14px;">17</span><span style="font-size:14px;">：</span><span style="font-size:14px;">00</span><span style="font-size:14px;">抵达仁川机场 办理离境手续，搭乘韩亚航空国际航班</span><b><span style="color:red;font-size:14px;">(19:30/22:30)</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;">返回桂林，结束愉快的旅行！</span><span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p style="margin-left:-53.95pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:31.5pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style="font-size:14px;">一</span></b> \r\n</p>', 4399, '桂林', 13, '双飞', 11, 7, 3, 1, 1, 4, NULL, NULL),
('Tour', 34, 240, 345, '', '每天08:00', '/attached/image/20120816/20120816093326_340.jpg', '漓江阳朔一日游', '<p style="background:white;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">早上</span><span style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">7:30—8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">：</span><span style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">30</span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">左右各酒店接客人，之后乘车前往磨盘山码头，乘坐空调船游览美丽的漓江，只见漓江两岸奇峰对峙、峭壁垂河、青山浮水、绿水逶迤。乘船游览其间，就好象在欣赏一幅徐徐展开的中国山水画的长卷，令人美不胜收。著名的景观有草坪幽洞、杨堤烟雨、浪石仙境、九马画山、黄布倒影、兴坪佳境。船行约四个半小时后到达阳朔码头。下午游览美丽的阳朔景色（月亮山、大榕树、聚龙谭、奇石宫、鉴山寺）。</span><span style="background:white;"> </span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">约</span><span style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">19</span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">：</span><span style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">30</span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">左右回到桂林</span><span style="background:white;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;">含：</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">空调船票、中餐、桂林—磨盘山码头、阳朔—桂林往返空调旅游大巴、导游服务费</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">阳朔陆地景点门票：聚龙潭、奇石宫、大榕树、月亮山、鉴山寺</span><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">不含：</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">码头电瓶车</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:14px;">节假日、黄金周价格请直接咨询客服</span></strong><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:14px;">。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span><b><span></span></b> \r\n</p>', 310, '不限', 2, '游船/大巴', 2, 1, 12, 1, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('Tour', 35, 140, 240, '', '每天08:00', '/attached/image/20120816/20120816093912_826.jpg', '兴坪渔村风光一日游', '<p style="background:white;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">早上约</span><span style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">：</span><span style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">00</span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">酒店接乘车前往阳朔，游览美丽的阳朔田园风光，观月亮山，看千年古榕树，中午在月亮山品尝正宗的阳朔农家菜，下午前往兴坪，游览美丽的漓江风光。乘船游览其间，就好象在欣赏一幅徐徐展开的中国山水画的长卷，令人美不胜收。之后可以前往兴坪渔村，美国前总统克林顿在这里留下的足迹。约</span><span style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">19</span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">：</span><span style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">30</span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">左右回到桂林</span><span style="background:white;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;">含：</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">船票、中餐、桂林—阳朔—兴坪—阳朔—桂林往返空调旅游大巴、导游服务费</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:26.25pt;background:white;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">阳朔陆地景点门票：聚龙潭、奇石宫、大榕树、月亮山、鉴山寺</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:26.25pt;background:white;">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:26.25pt;background:white;">\r\n	<br />\r\n<strong><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:14px;">节假日、黄金周价格请直接咨询客服</span></strong><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:14px;">。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span> \r\n</p>', 180, '不限', 4, '游船/大巴', 2, 1, 12, 2, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('Tour', 36, 145, 255, '', '每天08:00', '/attached/image/20120816/20120816094125_319.jpg', '桂林山水精华一日游', '<p style="background:white;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">早上</span><span style="font-size:14px;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">：</span><span style="font-size:14px;">00</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">左右酒店接，乘车前往桂林王城，感受桂林百年的历史。到刘三姐大观园观赏最具广西少数民族风情的歌舞。下午</span><span style="font-size:14px;">13</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">：</span><span style="font-size:14px;">00</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">乘船游览一轮明月挂天空的穿山、天热屏障南溪山、昂首挺胸斗鸡山、与之江相望的龟山、两山之间的塔山、北斗七星的七星山、桂林城徽象鼻山、半枕漓江的伏波山、江山会景处叠彩山，感受不一样的游览方式</span><span style="font-size:14px;">—</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">船游十大名山。于穿山公园中游览，欣赏穿山岩中特有的钟乳石，感受大自然的鬼斧神工。</span><span style="font-size:14px;">18</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">：</span><span style="font-size:14px;">00</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">结束行程</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="background:white;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;">含：</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;"><span style="font-size:14px;">市区景点车费、导游服务费、</span><span style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">象山十大名山水上游</span></span><span style="background:white;"> </span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">、靖江王府（独秀峰）</span><span style="background:white;"> </span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">、</span><span style="background:white;"> </span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">穿山公园（穿山岩）</span><span style="background:white;"> </span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">、刘三姐大观园</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="background:white;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="background:white;">\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:14px;">节假日、黄金周价格请直接咨询客服</span></strong><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:14px;">。</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;background:white;"></span><span style="background:white;"></span> \r\n</p>', 195, '不限', 2, '大巴', 1, 1, 12, 3, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('Tour', 38, 130, 198, '', '每天08:00', '/attached/image/20120816/20120816100510_25.jpg', '龙脊梯田一日游', '<p style="background:white;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">早约</span><span style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">：</span><span style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">00</span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">酒店接乘车前往全世界最大的人造梯田</span><span style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">—</span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:14px;">龙脊梯田，这是一条有如龙的脊背一样的梯田，伴有最原始最淳朴的少数民族风情，完全体现出少数民族的智慧和结晶。</span><span style="background:white;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;">含：</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">龙脊梯田门票、黄洛瑶寨、金竹壮寨门票桂林</span><span style="font-size:14px;">—</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">龙脊</span><span style="font-size:14px;">—</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">桂林往返空调旅游大巴、导游服务费。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">不含：转车费、长发表演</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:14px;">节假日、黄金周价格请直接咨询客服</span></strong><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:14px;">。</span><br />\r\n<b><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span><span></span></b> \r\n</p>', 180, '不限', 3, '大巴', 3, 1, 12, 5, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL);
