('Tour', 39, 155, 228, '', '每天19：00', '/attached/image/20120816/20120816143603_921.jpg', '印象•刘三姐', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">观看世界上最大的山水实景剧场，集漓江山水、</span> <span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">广西少数民族文化的代表—刘三姐、中国最具魅力的导演——张艺谋先生出任总导演。演出现场气势恢弘、内容新颖，观众无不赞不绝口！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;">含：</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">印象·刘三姐门票。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;">注：如需当天返回桂林，另加30元/人车费</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;"><strong><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:14px;">节假日、黄金周价格请直接咨询客服</span></strong><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:14px;">。</span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>', 175, '不限', 3, '大巴', 2, 1, 12, 6, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('Tour', 40, 120, 240, '', '每天08:00', '/attached/image/20120816/20120816144154_236.jpg', '乐满地休闲游', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">早上约</span><span>8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">：</span><span>00</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">左右酒店出发乘车前往兴安县游览著名的</span><span>“</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">中国迪士尼乐园</span><span>”——</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">乐满地主题乐园，乐满地主题乐园是一个类似于美国迪士尼乐园的大型娱乐场所。包括有美国西部区、中国城、梦幻世界、海盗村、南太平洋区等特色游乐景观区。能够为到桂林旅游的朋友提供完善、多样的娱乐空间。整个园区可观、可闻、可游、可赏、可疯狂。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;">含：</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">乐满地主题乐园门票、桂林</span><span>—</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">兴安</span><span>—</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">桂林往返空调旅游大巴、导游服务费</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><strong><span style="color:#E53333;">节假日、黄金周价格请直接咨询客服</span></strong><span style="color:#E53333;">。</span> <br />\r\n</span><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;"></span></b> \r\n</p>', 160, '不限', 3, '大巴', 4, 1, 12, 7, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('Tour', 41, 400, 550, '', '每天08:00', '/attached/image/20120816/20120816144428_600.jpg', '龙脊梯田、龙胜温泉二天一晚游', '<p style="background:white;">\r\n	<b><span style="background:white;">D1</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;background:white;">：</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;background:white;">早上约</span><span style="background:white;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:white;">：</span><span style="background:white;">00</span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:white;">酒店出发到龙脊梯田，途经金竹壮寨，黄洛瑶寨（自费参观黄洛歌舞表演），参观天下一绝的龙脊梯田，体验壮瑶风情。下午换车至龙胜温泉中心酒店入住中心宾馆，晚上泡温泉浴。</span><span style="background:white;"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:white;">住：龙胜温泉中心酒店（四星）</span><span style="background:white;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="background:white;">\r\n	<b><span style="background:white;">D2</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;background:white;">：</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;background:white;">早餐后自由活动，可以森林漫步，享受最新鲜的森林氧吧，中午乘车至龙胜路口，换车返回桂林，</span><span style="background:white;"> </span><span style="font-family:宋体;background:white;">结束桂林愉快的旅程。</span><span style="background:white;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;">含：</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">龙脊梯田门票、黄洛瑶寨门票、金竹壮寨门票、温泉门票、龙胜温泉中心酒店住宿</span><span>1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">晚、第二天中心酒店一早一正餐，桂林</span><span>—</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">龙脊</span><span>—</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">桂林往返空调旅游大巴、导游服务费。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;"><strong><span style="color:#E53333;">节假日、黄金周价格请直接咨询客服</span></strong><span style="color:#E53333;">。</span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>', 480, '不限', 2, '大巴', 3, 2