			<span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">早餐后，</span><b><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">自费</span></b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">太湖第一名胜</span><span style="color:#000000;">(</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">太湖佳绝处</span><span style="color:#000000;">)</span><b><span style="color:blue;"><span style="color:#000000;">【鼋头渚】</span><span style="color:#000000;">+</span><span style="color:#000000;">【梅园】或【锡惠公园】或【蠡园】（需另交当地导游</span><span style="color:#000000;">180</span><span style="color:#000000;">元</span><span style="color:#000000;">/</span><span style="color:#000000;">人联票） 。</span></span></b><span style="color:#000000;">车赴苏州，</span><span style="color:#000000;">游览</span></span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">游览姑苏城外的著名景区千年古刹</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">—</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">【</span></b></span><b><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">寒山寺】</span></b><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">感受张继《枫桥夜泊》的诗境。游览姑苏水乡风情的民俗园--</span><b><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">【定园】</span></b><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">（游览时间约50分钟）、观塔影湖、观花亭等景点。</span><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">晚可自愿自费夜游苏州古运河</span><span style="color:#000000;">120/</span><span style="color:#000000;">人</span><span style="color:#000000;">----</span><span style="color:#000000;">观二十座不同风格的苏州桥梁以及乾隆六下江南的御码头等，</span></span></b><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">入住酒店</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="36">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">早中晚</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="32">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">苏州</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="54">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">D4</span></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="638">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<b><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">园</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">林王国——苏州（苏州</span><u><span style="color:#000000;">150KM</span></u><span style="color:#000000;">乌镇</span><u><span style="color:#000000;">80KM</span></u><span style="color:#000000;">杭州）</span><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">早餐后，</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">游览乾隆六下江南的园林古镇</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;color:#000000;">--</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">水乡</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">【木渎】</span></b><span style="color:#000000;">（游览时间约</span></span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;color:#000000;">1.5</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">小时）（国家</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;color:#000000;">AAAA</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">级景区），含虹饮山房（江南皇家园林、古戏台、圣旨馆、科举馆等）、严家花园（江南私家园林的杰出代表）</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;color:#000000;">,</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">车赴桐乡，参观游览</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;color:#000000;">“</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">中国最后的枕水人家</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;color:#000000;">”</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">——</span><b><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">【乌镇】</span></b><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">江南水乡</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;color:#000000;">“</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">小桥、流水、人家</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;color:#000000;">”</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">的典范</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;color:#000000;">, </span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">影视片</span><span style="color:#000000;">[</span><span style="color:#000000;">似水年华</span><span style="color:#000000;">]</span><span style="color:#000000;">等的拍摄取景地。（</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">财神湾、百床馆、江南木雕陈列室、蓝印花布、矛盾故居、修真观戏台等）</span><span style="color:#000000;">,</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">晚上可自愿自费欣赏斥资六千万巨资打造的“给我一天，还你千年”世界三大民秀大型歌舞表演</span><span style="color:#000000;">----</span><span style="color:#000000;">宋城千古情</span><span style="color:#000000;">260/</span><span style="color:#000000;">人</span><span style="color:#000000;">-280/</span><span style="color:#000000;">人，</span><span style="color:#000000;">(</span><span style="color:#000000;">参加宋城各种民间活动，感受清明上河图的古老风韵）</span><span style="color:#000000;">。</span></b></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">或</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">晚自费游览【西湖之夜】（费用另付</span><span style="color:#000000;">240</span><span style="color:#000000;">元</span><span style="color:#000000;">/</span><span style="color:#000000;">人，逛杭州名品街、观赏大型西湖音乐喷泉及大型演出《西湖之夜》，</span></span></b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">后入住酒店。</span><b><span></span></b></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="36">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">早中晚</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="32">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">杭州</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="54">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">D5</span></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="638">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">人间天堂——杭州（杭州</span><u><span style="color:#000000;">160KM</span></u><span style="color:#000000;">上海）</span><span></span></span></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">早餐后，领杭州风月美</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">【漫步西湖】</span></b><span style="color:#000000;">游览</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">【花港观鱼、苏堤春晓】</span></b><span style="color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">1.5h</span><span style="color:#000000;">），</span></span><span style="color:#000000;">近距离欣赏西湖、远观三潭印月、阮墩环碧、游览红鱼池、御碑亭、牡丹亭、孔雀园。车赴上海，</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">自费</span><span style="color:#000000;">观赏</span><span style="color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">上海夜景（包含登</span><span style="color:#000000;">88</span><span style="color:#000000;">层金茂大厦</span><span style="color:#000000;">360</span><span style="color:#000000;">度俯瞰上海夜景</span><span style="color:#000000;">+</span><span style="color:#000000;">乘坐豪华游轮夜游上海母亲河黄浦江</span><span style="color:#000000;"> 240</span><span style="color:#000000;">元</span><span style="color:#000000;">/</span><span style="color:#000000;">人）体验夜上海的魅力。</span></span></b><span style="color:#000000;">入住酒店。</span></span><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="36">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">早中</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">X</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="32">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">上海</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="54">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">8</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">月</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">27</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">日</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="638">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">现代都市——上海</span><span></span></span></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">早餐后，游整治一新的</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">【外滩风光带】</span></b><span style="color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">20</span><span style="color:#000000;">分钟）</span></span><span style="color:#000000;">百年上海滩的标志和象征，万国建筑博览群、黄埔江风光。</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">【南京路步行街】</span></b><span style="color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">90</span><span style="color:#000000;">分钟）</span></span><span style="color:#000000;">老上海十里洋场，中华五星商业街，数以千计的大中小型商场，汇集了中国最全和最时尚的商品，自由观光购物。</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">【城隍庙】</span></b><span style="color:#000000;">自费品尝老上海的特色风味小吃。赠送</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">【</span></b><b><span style="color:#000000;">观光车票</span><span style="color:#000000;">】</span></b><span style="color:#000000;">游览</span><span style="color:#000000;">领略上海繁华，此次华东之旅画上圆满的句号，</span></span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">根据航班时间送团。浦东机场乘飞机</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;">9c8805</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">（预计</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;">20:30</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">起飞）返桂林。</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="36">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">早</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">XX</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="32">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;">/</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="54">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">标准</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td colspan="3" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="707">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">桂林<span>/</span>上海往返机票、</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">宾馆标准房（预备三星、空调、彩电、独立卫生间）</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">全程空调旅游车、景点首道大门票（自费景点除外）、含<span>5</span>早<span>6</span>正餐（正常餐标，<span>8</span>菜一汤，十人一桌，不足十人一桌按标准团餐表安排，菜量相应减少）、全程地陪中文讲解服务</span><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="54">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">购物</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td colspan="3" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="707">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">全程共六个购物安排，皆为华东地区有特色有代表的特产，导游员不得私自增加，请游客监督：<b><u><span style="color:purple;"><span style="color:#E53333;">无锡蠡湖紫砂馆（</span><span style="color:#E53333;">1h</span><span style="color:#E53333;">）</span></span></u><span style="color:purple;"><span style="color:#E53333;">、</span><u><span style="color:#E53333;">苏州新东吴淡水珍珠馆（</span><span style="color:#E53333;">1h</span><span style="color:#E53333;">）</span></u><span style="color:#E53333;">、</span><u><span style="color:#E53333;">杭州丝绸展览中心（</span><span style="color:#E53333;">1h</span><span style="color:#E53333;">）</span></u><span style="color:#E53333;">、</span><u><span style="color:#E53333;">杭州茶乡人家（</span><span style="color:#E53333;">1h</span><span style="color:#E53333;">）</span></u><span style="color:#E53333;">、</span><u><span style="color:#E53333;">上海蒂泰尼水晶开采集团（</span><span style="color:#E53333;">1h</span><span style="color:#E53333;">）</span></u><span style="color:#E53333;">、</span><u><span style="color:#E53333;">上海希尔曼刀具馆（</span><span style="color:#E53333;">1h</span><span style="color:#E53333;">）</span></u><span style="color:#E53333;">。</span></span></b></span><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="54">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">友情推荐</span></b><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;"></span></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td colspan="3" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="707">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">以下项目为公司推荐的旅游项目，游客自愿参加，持任何证件都不再优惠。</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">不参加游客在门口车里等待或周边自由活动。</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;color:black;"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:0cm;">\r\n						<b><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:新宋体;color:#E53333;"><span style="color:#E53333;">1、</span></span></b><b><u><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;color:purple;"><span style="color:#E53333;">苏州：古运河：</span><span style="color:#E53333;">120</span><span style="color:#E53333;">元</span><span style="color:#E53333;">/</span><span style="color:#E53333;">人，观二十座不同风格的苏州桥梁以及乾隆六下江南的御码头等</span><span><span style="color:#E53333;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="color:#E53333;">2.</span></span><span style="color:#E53333;">杭州：宋城千古情：</span><span style="color:#E53333;">260--280</span><span style="color:#E53333;">元</span><span style="color:#E53333;">/</span><span style="color:#E53333;">人，包含宋城门票及“给我一天还你千年”大型歌舞表演 或 【西湖之夜】（费用另付</span><span style="color:#E53333;">240</span><span style="color:#E53333;">元</span><span style="color:#E53333;">/280</span><span style="color:#E53333;">元</span><span style="color:#E53333;">/</span><span style="color:#E53333;">人</span><span style="color:#E53333;">3.</span><span style="color:#E53333;">上海：上海夜景（登环球</span><span style="color:#E53333;">+</span><span style="color:#E53333;">黄浦江夜游</span><span style="color:#E53333;">240</span><span style="color:#E53333;">元</span><span style="color:#E53333;">/</span><span style="color:#E53333;">人）体验夜上海的魅力。</span><span style="color:#E53333;">4.</span><span style="color:#E53333;">灵山：</span><span style="color:#E53333;">210</span><span style="color:#E53333;">元</span><span style="color:#E53333;">/</span><span style="color:#E53333;">人</span><span style="color:#E53333;"><span style="color:#E53333;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color:#E53333;">或</span><span style="color:#E53333;"><span style="color:#E53333;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color:#E53333;">鼋头渚</span><span style="color:#E53333;">+</span><span style="color:#E53333;">梅园</span><span style="color:#E53333;">/</span><span style="color:#E53333;">锡惠公园</span><span style="color:#E53333;">/</span><span style="color:#E53333;">蠡园</span><span><span style="color:#E53333;">&nbsp; </span><span style="color:#E53333;">180</span></span><span style="color:#E53333;">元</span><span style="color:#E53333;">/</span><span style="color:#E53333;">人</span></span></u></b><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#E53333;">★</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:新宋体;color:#E53333;">（自费项目任何证件均无优惠，大人、小孩同等价格，自费项目若不参加者，则在导游指定地点或者景点附近自由活动，活动时间为自费项目参观游览时间）</span><b><u><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;color:purple;"></span></u></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="54">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<b><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">须知<span></span></span></b> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td colspan="3" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="707">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">1</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">、因入住宾馆登记和乘飞机需要，所有游客须带好身份证等有效证件；旺季住宿可能较偏，正常行程内我社安排空调旅游车<span></span></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">2</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">、所有证件如：导游证、军官证、老年证军残证等有效证件在景点内不享受任何优惠<span></span></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="margin-left:13.5pt;text-indent:-13.5pt;">\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">3</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">、在不减少景点的情况下，我社可调整行程 。如遇人力不可抗拒因素造成无法游览的景点我社只负责退还团队门票价差额，不承担由此造成的损失和责任。游客因个人原因临时放弃游览，用餐，及住宿等，我社一概不退费用。<span style="color:red;">（注：不参加自费景点的游客导游负责安排在车内休息或周边自由活动。小孩不享受优惠！自费景点含车费）。</span><span></span></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="margin-left:13.5pt;text-indent:-13.5pt;">\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">4</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">、团队餐<span>10</span>人一桌，<span>8</span>菜<span>1</span>汤，若人数不足<span>10</span>人则菜量相应减少；若有少数民族客人不用餐，餐费不退<span>5</span>、客人报名人数系单数，我社尽量安排拼住或三人间如果无法协调，需由客人承担产生的单房差，房差<span>100</span>元<span>/</span>间<span>/</span>晚。<span></span></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="margin-left:13.5pt;text-indent:-13.5pt;">\r\n						<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">7</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">、</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;">团队机票不的改签、不得变更、不得退票，参见春秋航空客规。</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;"><span>&nbsp; </span>8</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;">、因是全国散客拼团，所以可能会需要等待其他散客的情况，希望大家能够耐心等待！<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>9</span>、请客人认真填写质访单，一切问题以质访单为准，行程结束后不接受相关问题投诉。<span></span></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</div>', 1680, '桂林', 2, '飞机/大巴', 1, 7, 14, 2, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tour` (`dtype`, `id`, `children`, `door_price`, `feature`, `group_date`, `image`, `name`, `plan`, `privilege`, `start_city`, `version`, `way`, `address`, `tour_day`, `type`, `sort`, `recommend`, `city_id`, `description`, `keywords`) VALUES
('Tour', 52, 4030, 6000, '<p style="margin-left:28.5pt;text-indent:30.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;">此条线路，属于丝绸之路甘肃、青海的精华部分，其深厚的历史文化底蕴，文明世界的敦煌莫高窟艺术，叹为观止的美丽的自然风光，戈壁、雪山、高原湖泊、沙漠、海市蜃楼……都会让你沉迷其<span><span>&nbsp; </span></span>中而流连忘返！</span><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;">一、往返大交通<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;">二、<span>行程中有闻名于世的“敦煌学”发源地——敦煌莫高窟，有中国最大最美的高原咸水湖——青海湖，有藏传佛教黄教格鲁派六大尊主寺之一的——塔尔寺<span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;">三、行程中走到的城市：兰州——是中国陆地板块的几何中心，是黄土高原黄土覆盖最后的地方；是著名的瓜果之乡，是著名小吃——兰州牛肉拉面的发源地；西宁——号称为中国的“夏都”，是著名的避暑胜地。。。。。</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:black;">这些是否已经有了足够吸引你去的理由……！</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;">。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;">四、六天两个购物点安排，敦煌地矿陈列馆可以欣赏到“夜光杯”，敦煌果脯厂可以品尝到地道的当地产的非常甜的水果制作而成的果脯，青海藏药博物馆里可以揭开神秘的藏药发展历史、藏药材标本。。。。。。。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:文鼎海報體;">【</span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:宋体;">风味推荐</span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:文鼎海報體;">】</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;">敦煌雪山骆掌 兰州牛肉拉面、清真羊羔肉、灰豆子、甜醅子、羊肉泡馍、烤羊肉串<span><span>&nbsp; </span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:文鼎海報體;color:black;">【住宿特色】</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:black;">敦煌、西宁安排市中心三星酒店，让您住的舒适、轻松。<span> </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:文鼎海報體;">【</span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:宋体;">好礼相送</span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:文鼎海報體;">】</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;">◆贴心为您准备每天每人一瓶矿泉水<span> </span></span> \r\n</p>', '8月3日 ，10日， 17日， 24日、31日', '/attached/image/20120820/20120820095452_869.png', '兰州敦煌西宁5晚6天双飞双卧', '<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">第一天</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">：</span></b><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">桂林</span></b><span style="font-family:Arial;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;color:#000000;">- </span><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">西安</span></b><span style="font-family:Arial;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;color:#000000;"> <span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">-</span></span><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">兰州</span></b><span style="font-family:Arial;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;color:#000000;">-</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">敦煌</span></b><b><span style="font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333;background:#E5E5E5;"> <span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:#E5E5E5;">不含</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">餐<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>宿<span>:</span>火车空调硬卧</span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;"><span>&nbsp; </span></span><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新宋体;color:#993300;"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">于桂林机场乘机<span>MU2330(10:30-12:15) </span>至西安转<span>HU7650(17:05-18:05)</span>赴兰州，接机后乘车赴市区，沿途观兰州市容市貌，晚餐后乘火车赴敦煌。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">兰州机场<span>/</span>市区<span> 100KM<span>&nbsp; </span></span>高速\r\n约<span>1.5</span>小时<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:39.95pt;text-indent:-39.95pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">第二天</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">：</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;">敦煌</span></b><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">一日游</span></b><span style="font-family:Arial;background:#E5E5E5;"></span><b><span style="font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333;background:#E5E5E5;"> <span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span> </span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:#E5E5E5;">含早中晚</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">餐<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>宿<span>:</span>敦煌<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">早抵柳园火车站<span>.</span>乘车前往敦煌市区，用早餐后，参观</span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:red;">鸣沙山、月牙泉</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">（距市区<span>10KM</span>，约<span>15</span>分钟，参观需时<span>3</span>小时左右）沙丘 因人登之即鸣，泉水形成一湖，在沙丘环抱之中酷似一<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">湾新月而得名，一处神奇的沙漠奇观。午餐后参观中国四大佛教石窟之一</span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:red;">莫高窟</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">（<span>160</span>元，距市区<b><span>2</span></b><span>5</span>公里，约半小时可抵，参观需时<span>2.5</span>小时左右），</span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">参观果脯厂</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">（<span>30</span>分钟）品尝各<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">类果脯<span>，晚餐后入住酒店。<span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">柳园<span>/</span>敦煌<span> 120KM </span>行车约<span>2.5</span>小时<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">自费项目</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">：骑骆驼<span>80</span>元，电瓶车<span>10</span>元<span>/</span>人<span>,</span>滑沙<span>20</span>元<span>/</span>人<span>,</span>鞋套<span>:10</span>元<span>/</span>人<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">购物安排</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">：敦煌果脯厂 约<span>40</span>分钟</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">第三天</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">：</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;">敦煌</span></b><span style="font-family:Arial;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;">-</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">玉门关</span></b><span style="font-family:Arial;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;">-</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">雅丹</span></b><span style="font-family:Arial;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;">-</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">敦煌</span></b><span style="font-family:Arial;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;">-</span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;">兰州</span></b><b><span style="font-family:Wingdings;background:#E5E5E5;"> <span style="color:#333333;"><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:#E5E5E5;">含早中晚</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">餐<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>宿<span>:</span>火车空调硬卧</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span></span><span style="background:#E5E5E5;"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n</span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">早餐后乘汽车前往<b><span style="color:red;">玉门关</span></b></span><span>--</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">汉代西陲两关之一，是丝绸古道西出敦煌进入西域北道的必经关口，自古为中原进入西域之门户。<b><span style="color:red;">敦煌雅丹地质公园</span></b></span><span>,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">—迄今为止在世界范围内所发现的规模最大、发育最成熟、形象最好、最具代表性的雅丹地貌群落，是敦煌的又一自然地理奇观，曾在这里拍摄过《英雄》、《天脉传奇》、《齐天大圣</span><span>--</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">孙悟空》、刘德华主演的《三国》等多部影片，参观后乘汽车返回市区，</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">晚餐后乘</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">车赴敦煌火车站乘火车赴兰州。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:black;">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">敦煌</span><span style="color:black;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">玉门关单程</span><span style="color:black;">110</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">公里</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">，车程约</span><span style="color:black;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">小时，游览约</span><span style="color:black;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">小时</span><span style="color:black;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">玉门关</span><span style="color:black;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">雅丹单程</span><span style="color:black;">80</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">公里</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">，车程约</span><span style="color:black;">1.5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">小时，游览约</span><span style="color:black;">1-1.5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">小时</span><span style="color:black;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:新宋体-18030;color:black;">自费项目：越野车<span>500-700</span>元<span>/</span>车<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:新宋体-18030;color:black;">购物安排：无<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:新宋体-18030;color:black;">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">第四天</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">：<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">兰州</span></span></b><span style="font-family:Arial;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;color:#000000;">-</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">青海湖</span></b><span style="font-family:Arial;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;color:#000000;">-</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">西宁</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Webdings;color:#333333;background:#E5E5E5;"> <span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333;background:#E5E5E5;"><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:#E5E5E5;">含早中晚</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">餐<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>宿<span>:</span>西宁</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新宋体-18030;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:新宋体;">抵达兰州早餐品尝兰州风味拉面，赏兰州市容市貌后乘汽车赴西宁，沿途欣赏黄土高原农田风光，中餐后参观中国最大最美的高原咸水湖泊——<b><span style="color:red;">青海湖</span></b><span style="color:black;">（约<span>1.5</span>小时）夏季的青海湖边万亩油菜花田仿佛让您置身于世外桃园，后</span>途经青藏咽喉<span>-</span>湟源峡谷，远观黄土高原与青藏高原的分界线<span>-</span>日月山（山口海拔<span>3520</span>米），唐朝文成公主与吐蕃赞普松赞干布联姻，正是由此向南经唐蕃古道进入西藏的。经过<span>“</span>天下河水皆向东，唯有此溪向西流<span>”</span>的倒淌河。后乘汽车返回西宁晚餐后入住酒店。<span> </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:新宋体;">兰州<span>/</span>西宁<span> 250KM </span>高速 行车约<span>3</span>小时，西宁<span>/</span>青海湖<span> 150KM </span>省道 行车约<span>2</span>小时<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:新宋体;">自费项目：游船<span>80</span>元<span>/</span>人，电瓶车<span>10</span>元，互助风情园：<span>50</span>元<span>/</span>人<span> </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:新宋体;">购物安排<span>:</span>无<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:新宋体;">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">第五天</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">：<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">西宁</span></span></b><span style="font-family:Arial;background:#E5E5E5;"></span><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">-兰州</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Webdings;color:#333333;background:#E5E5E5;"> <span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333;background:#E5E5E5;"><span>&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:#E5E5E5;">含早中晚</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">餐<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>宿<span>:兰州</span></span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新宋体;"><span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">早餐后参观游览藏传佛教黄教格鲁派六大宗主寺之——<b><span style="color:red;">塔尔寺</span></b><span style="color:black;">(</span><span style="color:black;">约<span>2</span>小时<span>)</span></span><b>，</b></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;">塔尔寺</span><span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;font-weight:normal;">以<span>“</span>艺术三绝<span>”</span>—堆绣、壁画、酥油花闻名于世，通过参观了解藏传佛教、黄教的历史以及名人趣事；</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">中餐后参观藏医药博物馆，乘汽车返回兰州，游览黄河四十公里黄河旅游风情线，兰州标志性雕塑建筑——黄河母亲像雕塑、黄河上游过去年代古老的倒提黄河水灌溉工具——<b><span style="color:red;">黄河古水车</span></b><span style="color:black;">（<span>20</span>分钟）、</span><b><span style="color:red;">天下黄河第一桥——中山桥</span></b><span style="color:black;">（约<span>10</span>分钟）</span><b>，</b>用晚餐后入住酒店。 <b><u><span style="color:#993300;"></span></u></b></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">西宁<span>/</span>塔尔寺<span> 40KM </span>省道\r\n约<span>1</span>小时，西宁<span>/</span>兰州<span>250KM</span>高速约<span>3</span>小时<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">自费项目<span>:</span>羊皮筏子漂流<span>70</span>元<span>/</span>人<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">购物按排：藏医药博物馆（<span>30</span>分钟）<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">&nbsp;</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">第六天</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">：</span></b><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">兰州送团</span></b><span style="font-family:Arial;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;color:#000000;">-</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">西安</span></b><span style="font-family:Arial;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;font-size:14px;color:#000000;">-</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;"> </span><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #E5E5E5;">桂林</span></b><b><span style="font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333;background:#E5E5E5;"> <span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:#E5E5E5;">含早</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;background:#E5E5E5;">餐<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">早餐后</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">乘车赴机场搭乘班机<span>MU2305(12:35-13:40)</span>至西安转乘<span>MU2145(17:40-19:30)</span>返回桂林，结束愉快的西部之旅，返回甜蜜的家<span>!</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">兰州<span>/</span>中川机场<span> 100KM<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>车程约<span>1.5</span>小时</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">接待标准：</span><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、三星级或同级双人标准间，</span><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、区间空调旅游车、优秀导游服务。</span><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:14.7pt;text-indent:-14.7pt;">\r\n	<span>3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、全程</span><span>5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">早</span><span>8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">正餐（</span><span>20</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元</span><span>/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">正、正餐八菜一汤二道主食、十人一桌，人数不足菜量减少）</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、火车空调硬卧（含二程火车硬卧，如需软卧需补差价</span><span>280</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元</span><span>/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人）。</span><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、首道门票（不含骑马、骑骆驼、滑沙等其他自费项目）。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、自理南宁</span><span>/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">兰州</span><span>/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">南宁二程民航航班，含机建燃油。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、接团标识：各地导游举“大西北风景线”站牌或导游旗接站。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、兰州</span><span>/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">兰州机场若客人少于四人</span><span>,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">我社将派导游和客人乘民航大巴赴机场接团和送团。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">&nbsp;</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">备注：<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:26.15pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#3F3F3F;"><span>1、<span></span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;">此线路为团散线路，请提前<span>10</span>个工作日报名。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:26.15pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#3F3F3F;"><span>2、<span></span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;">机票一经开出，不得签转，不得退票。请带好有效身份证件或旅行证件。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:26.15pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#3F3F3F;"><span>3、<span></span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;">若受交通、气候、当地接待容量等原因影响，我社有权调整行程（景点不减少）或取消原定旅游计划。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:26.15pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#3F3F3F;"><span>4、<span></span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;">行程中客房为双标间，若出现单男单女我社将作为加床或补房差处理，请组团社遇此情况请提前告知客人。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:26.15pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#3F3F3F;"><span>5、<span></span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;">客人如自愿放弃行程中的提供标准，则不退任何费用（餐费、门票等）。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:26.15pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#3F3F3F;"><span>6、<span></span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;">以上旅游景点对学生证、老人证有一定的优惠政策，但以上价格已按折扣价计算成本，故客人不再享受景点门口所标示的优惠\r\n折扣！如客人某个景点不去参观，则一律不退景点的费用。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:26.15pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#3F3F3F;"><span>7、<span></span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;">自费项目我社导游不会强制推介，如有<span>50%</span>的客人参加，请不参加的客人在车外等。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:26.15pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-21.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#3F3F3F;"><span>8、<span></span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;">儿童费用不含床位、火车票、门票，如发生其它费用请家长现付。儿童火车硬卧<span>596</span>元（二程）</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:4.9pt;text-indent:20.1pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;">特别提示：为了防范您在旅游中的风险，保障您的切身利益，我们建议您购买旅游意外保险！！！<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;"><span>&nbsp;</span></span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:176.65pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:15.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑;">丝 路 旅 游 注 意 事 项</span></b><b><span style="font-size:15.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑;"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:15.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:15.0pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;">丝绸之路，作为集历史、文化、民族风情、塞外风光于一体的独特完整旅游区，正越来越受到世界各地旅游者的青睐，但丝路之行必须注意以下各项：<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:14.75pt;text-indent:-14.75pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">西北早晚温差较大，达到<span>10</span>度左右，须带厚外套或毛衣等较厚衣物，尤其在山区<span>8</span>月晚间气温下降到<span>5</span>－<span>10</span>度左右，一定要做好防寒工作，晚上睡觉时应将空调开到适度，不要过凉，或睡觉时不盖棉被，造成身体不适。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:14.75pt;text-indent:-14.75pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">2</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">因</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">西北地域辽阔，坐车时间较长，很多情况，须旅游者下车行走或亲自体验骑马、骑骆驼的乐趣。所以，一双合适的鞋显得尤为重要，在参加一些特殊的活动（如骑马、坐游船）时请选择合适的衣着。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:14.75pt;text-indent:-14.75pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">3</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">西北气温虽较内地略低，但因西北很多地区海拔较高，紫外线照射强烈。所以旅游者应准备充足有效的防晒品，同时配备清热、解渴、滋润的药物或冲剂，如王老吉、夏桑菊冲剂、十滴水等，以免一时难以承受过于干燥和酷热的气候。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:14.75pt;text-indent:-14.75pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">4</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">在</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">西北旅游，因行程较长、较为辛苦，气候差别过大，旅游者一时难以适应，可能会出现水土不服症状，旅游者应携带有关药物及一些常备治病药物，如创可贴、感冒药或治疗肠胃不适药物等。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:14.75pt;text-indent:-14.75pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">5</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">西北是多种少数民族地区，宗教色彩浓厚，信仰伊斯兰教的民族不吃猪肉等，这是他们在生活中最大的禁忌，绝对不可以冒犯，在西北饮食主要以牛羊肉为主，我们会尽量满足与客人的口味，但有些经济欠发达地区受到经济及宗教影响，没有汉餐或用餐口味比较单一，请多多克服！！！<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:14.75pt;text-indent:-14.75pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">6</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">整个旅途中，团友要注意保管好自己的财物：不要把手提电脑、照相机等贵重物品放在房间内，请寄存于总台；在游览途中或者晚上结伴出游的时候，请注意保管随身现金、手机等财物，以免造成不必要的损失，影响以后行程。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;">7</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;">、</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">民族工艺小刀新颖精致，民航与铁路部门均不准托运，只能通过邮局邮寄，请游客注意。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:14.75pt;text-indent:-14.75pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">8</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">与全国各地一样，使用北京时间，但与内地有<span>2</span>小时的时差，相应的作息时间也比内地推后两小时，游客需要自我调整；特别是起床、用餐等方面，请客人注意区别。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:14.75pt;text-indent:-14.75pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">9</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">大西北地区<span>,</span>自然环境<span>,</span>经济基础<span>,</span>和接待条件等相对内地有一定的差距（例如住宿标准，不能以华东地区的三星标准去衡量当地的三星宾馆）<span>.</span>出门在外<span>,</span>请大家保持平常的心态<span>,</span>外出旅游肯定不会象居家时一般的舒适<span>,</span>遇事不要急噪<span>,</span>请大家相互体谅、互相帮助<span>.</span>旅游的车程比较长<span>,</span>相对其他地区比较艰苦<span>,</span>要注意休息好<span>,</span>以保持充沛的精力和体力<span>.</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:14.75pt;text-indent:-14.75pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">10</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">由于是少数民族地区，购买东西时，如遇少数民族商贩，切记先谈好价格在买，如果不打算买千万不能跟商贩讨价还价或者随意触碰商品，以避免造成不必要的麻烦而引起不快。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:19.7pt;text-indent:-19.7pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">11</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">少数民族地区，口味以清真餐为主，可能会不太符合内地客人的饮食习惯，请大家做好心里准备。都是摊贩经营，卫生状况无法保证，因此请客人在食用时根据自身身体状况量力而行。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:19.7pt;text-indent:-19.7pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">12</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">、在骑马时，要听马夫安排，骑马的游客一定要注意安全，骑马过程中，不要用力抽打马匹，以免马受惊，看好骑马的时间，出发前一定要谈好价格，以免因为时间问题发生纠纷，上马时不要站在马后，不要拍马屁股，以防踢伤。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:19.7pt;text-indent:-19.7pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">13</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;">旅行社会按照约定安排购物店，但是由于很多景区有自己的购物点，而且是进入景区的必经之路，不属于旅行社安排范畴之内，鉴于其购物质量不能保证，请客人在购买时慎重考虑。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></b> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 5730, '桂林', 2, '飞机/火车/大巴', 1, 7, 14, 3, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('Tour', 53, NULL, 800, '<p>\r\n	靖江王府、遇龙河、兴坪渔村、冠岩、古东瀑布、市内水上精华游\r\n</p>', '每日', '/attached/image/20120820/20120820100255_635.jpg', '桂林夏日激情亲水最佳游', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">D1<span>、</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">抵达桂林（以中午前到达为例）</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">游览集桂林历史文化及山水精华于一体的<strong>【靖江王府】</strong></span><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">（</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">游览约<span>70</span><span>分钟）（含靖江王府、游览南天一柱独秀峰，靖江王城王府也是中国目前最大的也是保存最完好的番王府。）在市区游船码头乘船观看象鼻山、伏波山、叠彩山、穿山、斗鸡山等【市区水上游】</span></span><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span><span style="color:#333333;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">（</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">游览约<span>90</span><span>分钟），从另一个角度感受桂林别样风景。&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;住桂林</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">D2<span>、</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">早上接客人，乘车赴阳朔最美丽的兴坪古镇，&nbsp;体会<span>“</span><span>桂林山水甲天下，果然佳胜在兴坪</span><span>”</span><span>的兴坪佳景。乘船游览兴坪风光，游中国第一位总统孙中山、美国总统克林顿专程访&nbsp;问过的<strong>【兴坪渔村风光</strong><strong>】</strong></span></span><span style="color:#0000FF;font-size:9pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">（游程约<span>90</span><span>分钟）没有了游览全程漓江的长时间乘船的无聊等待，沿途经兴坪古镇、欣赏兴坪佳境。</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">游览阳朔精华景区阳朔阳朔田园风光最佳处阳朔必游处【遇龙河竹筏休闲游】</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">于迷人的山水之间，独特的田园山水，定让你惊喜不已。在清澈见底的遇龙河上打水仗、嬉水，或躺在竹筏的躺椅上悠哉游哉，好不惬意。</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;住桂林</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">D3<span>、</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">早上<span>8</span><span>点左右桂林各大酒店接团，乘车前往<strong>【冠岩景区</strong><strong>】</strong></span></span><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:9pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span style="color:#000000;">，</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">冠岩素有漓江上的明珠之称，有两项大世界吉尼斯纪录之最，岩洞游览方式之最，最长的旅游观光滑道。冠岩景区周围的田园风光，山、水、田一色。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><br />\r\n</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">然后游览全国唯一由地下涌泉汇集形成的多级串连瀑布，可走瀑戏浪的<strong>【古东瀑布景区】</strong></span><span style="color:#0000FF;font-size:9pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">景区融合了幽瀑、碧潭、原始生态、地质奇观、清新空气为一体，感受进入大自然拥抱的温馨，呼吸清新空气缓解工作疲劳。下午5点半左右返回桂林,结束冠岩古东瀑布一日游愉快行程(这条线路是近年来桂林比较火热比较受欢迎的,特别是暑假更是重点推荐项目)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【温馨提示】：</strong>1、以上报价为10人报价，人数变动会因为车费的平摊而有所变动，请咨询24小时热线。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2<span>、冠岩景区较大，从大门到溶洞交通需游客自理。滑倒或者电瓶车65元/人往返。古东瀑布景区如果游客选择攀爬瀑布游览需 要强制性租用景区内安全设施费用5元</span>/人。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3、免责条款：如遇洪水或其他原因，如旺季和会议包场等原因。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4、行程中没有任何强制加点以及强制购物消费项目。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5、本行程为样板，内容可以调整，详情请咨询。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【费用包含】</strong> <br />\r\n1、门票：兴坪渔村、遇龙河漂流、冠岩景区、古东瀑布景区<span><a href="http://www.guilintravel88.com/article/show-sight.asp?id=86"><span><br />\r\n</span></a></span>2、住宿：含2晚住宿，三星标准，每晚的酒店两人入住一间双人标准间，如出现单房差需补交房费。 <br />\r\n3、交通：全程空调旅游车&nbsp; <br />\r\n4、导游：优秀导游讲解服务费<br />\r\n5、保险：包含旅行社责任保险 <br />\r\n<strong>【费用不含】</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n1、团队用餐：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A、单独开餐，游客可根据个人喜好自主决定，自由选择风味特色点菜；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;B、由旅行社或导游推荐安排包餐，标准为早餐5元/人正餐15元/人（10人/桌人数不够份量酌减）；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n2、景区交通：景区内缆车、索道、观光小火车、电梯等代步工具费用；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n3、大交通费：不含游客所在地区往返桂林的机票、火车票等大交通费用；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n4、其他费用：个人的消费、自费项目及因不可抗力因素所产生的额外费用等；\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【预订须知</strong>】：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9pt;">1</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">、 请您最迟提前一天向我们预订，旅游旺季及黄金周提前<span>5</span>到<span>10</span>天以上向我们预订<span>(</span>黄金周期间费用上浮<span>100%~200%</span>，请关注本网站变更<span>)</span>。<span><br />\r\n3</span>、 在不减少行程内景点的情况下，我公司有权根据实际情况对行程游览顺序做出相应调整；<span><br />\r\n4</span>、 各种报价标准之间的区别只限于酒店住宿，其他旅游接待服务均相同；<span><span>&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n5</span>、 如遇相关单位价格做出政策性调整则以当时价格为准，恕不另行通知；<span> <br />\r\n6</span>、 游客报名<span>,</span>请将姓名<span>,</span>人数<span>,</span>抵达航班号<span>,</span>车次<span>,</span>时间及联系电话等相关资料通过预定系统<span>,E-mail,</span>电话或传真或网上留言等形式告知我公司<span>,</span>我们将在<span>24</span>小时内与您联系并确认。<span><br />\r\n7</span>、 为确保游客合法权益，公司将和游客签定正式旅游合同。<span><br />\r\n8</span>、 如有不详，敬请来电、<span>QQ</span>、<span>MSN</span>垂询。 <span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:ˎ̥;font-size:9pt;">9</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">、接站</span><span style="font-family:ˎ̥;font-size:9pt;">(</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">接机</span><span style="font-family:ˎ̥;font-size:9pt;">)</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">方式：请看手持写有您名字的接站牌，就是我社的安排的接待工作人员，您可以安全的接受她的服务。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 800, '桂林', 4, '大巴', 1, 3, 13, 4, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL);
