('Tour', 54, NULL, 670, '<p>\r\n	遇龙河、兴坪渔村、冠岩、古东瀑布\r\n</p>', '每日', '/attached/image/20120820/20120820101837_146.jpg', '桂林印象·时尚生态游', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">D1<span>、</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">中午或者下午接团<span>,</span><span>入住酒店</span><span>,</span><span>可自行游览桂林市内。座座新桥，景趣相融，各呈异彩，楼亭台榭，错落有致，交相辉映，万盏齐明，灯火阑珊，双塔映月，桥跨银河，宋街连城。体现了桂林的特点</span><span>“</span><span>景在城中，城在景中</span><span>”</span><span>。</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>住桂林</strong></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">D2<span>、</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">早上接客人，乘车赴阳朔最美丽的兴坪古镇，&nbsp;体会<span>“</span><span>桂林山水甲天下，果然佳胜在兴坪</span><span>”</span><span>的兴坪佳景。乘船游览兴坪风光，游中国第一位总统孙中山、美国总统克林顿专程访&nbsp;问过的<strong>【兴坪渔村风光</strong><strong>】</strong></span></span><span style="color:#0000FF;font-size:9pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span><span style="color:#0000FF;font-size:9pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">（游程约<span>90</span><span>分钟）没有了游览全程漓江的长时间乘船的无聊等待，沿途经兴坪古镇、欣赏兴坪佳境。</span></span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">游览阳朔精华景区阳朔阳朔田园风光最佳处阳朔必游处<strong>【遇龙河竹筏休闲游】</strong></span><span><a href="http://www.guilintravel.cn/article/show-sight.asp?id=46"><span style="color:#0000FF;text-decoration:underline;font-size:9pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span></a></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">穿梭于迷人的山水之间，独特的田园山水，定让你惊喜不已。在清澈见底的遇龙河上打水仗、嬉水，或躺在竹筏的躺椅上悠哉游哉，好不惬意。</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;住桂林</strong></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">D3<span>、</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">早上<span>8</span><span>点左右桂林各大酒店接团，乘车前往<strong>【冠岩景区</strong><strong>】</strong>，</span></span><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">冠岩素有漓江上的明珠之称，有两项大世界吉尼斯纪录之最，岩洞游览方式之最，最长的旅游观光滑道。冠岩景区周围的田园风光，山、水、田一色。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><br />\r\n</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">然后游览全国唯一由地下涌泉汇集形成的多级串连瀑布，可走瀑戏浪的<strong>【古东瀑布景区】</strong></span><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">景区融合了幽瀑、碧潭、原始生态、地质奇观、清新空气为一体，感受进入大自然拥抱的温馨，呼吸清新空气缓解工作疲劳。下午5点半左右返回桂林,结束冠岩古东瀑布一日游愉快行程</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【温馨提示】：</strong>1、以上报价为10人报价，人数变动会因为车费的平摊而有所变动，请咨询24小时热线。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2<span>、冠岩景区较大，从大门到溶洞交通需游客自理。滑倒或者电瓶车65元/人往返。古东瀑布景区如果游客选择攀爬瀑布游览需 要强制性租用景区内安全设施费用5元</span>/人。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3、免责条款：如遇洪水或其他原因，如旺季和会议包场等原因，不能观看《印象刘三姐》演出的，将按照门票价格退还票款给游客。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4、行程中没有任何强制加点以及强制购物消费项目。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5、本行程为样板，内容可以调整，详情请咨询。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【费用包含】</strong> <br />\r\n1、门票：兴坪渔村、遇龙河漂流、冠岩景区、古东瀑布景区<span><a href="http://www.guilintravel88.com/article/show-sight.asp?id=86"><span><br />\r\n</span></a></span>2、住宿：含2晚住宿，每晚的酒店两人入住一间双人标准间，如出现单房差需补交房费。 <br />\r\n3、交通：全程空调旅游车&nbsp; <br />\r\n4、导游：优秀导游讲解服务费<br />\r\n5、保险：包含旅行社责任保险 <br />\r\n<strong>【费用不含】</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n1、团队用餐：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A、单独开餐，游客可根据个人喜好自主决定，自由选择风味特色点菜；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;B、由旅行社或导游推荐安排包餐，标准为早餐5元/人正餐15元/人（10人/桌人数不够份量酌减）；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n2、景区交通：景区内缆车、索道、观光小火车、电梯等代步工具费用；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n3、大交通费：不含游客所在地区往返桂林的机票、火车票等大交通费用；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n4、其他费用：个人的消费、自费项目及因不可抗力因素所产生的额外费用等；\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【预订须知</strong>】：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9pt;">1</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">、 请您最迟提前一天向我们预订，旅游旺季及黄金周提前<span>5</span>到<span>10</span>天以上向我们预订<span>(</span>黄金周期间费用上浮<span>100%~200%</span>，请关注本网站变更<span>)</span>。<span><br />\r\n3</span>、 在不减少行程内景点的情况下，我公司有权根据实际情况对行程游览顺序做出相应调整；<span><br />\r\n4</span>、 各种报价标准之间的区别只限于酒店住宿，其他旅游接待服务均相同；<span><span>&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n5</span>、 如遇相关单位价格做出政策性调整则以当时价格为准，恕不另行通知；<span> <br />\r\n6</span>、 游客报名<span>,</span>请将姓名<span>,</span>人数<span>,</span>抵达航班号<span>,</span>车次<span>,</span>时间及联系电话等相关资料通过预定系统<span>,E-mail,</span>电话或传真或网上留言等形式告知我公司<span>,</span>我们将在<span>24</span>小时内与您联系并确认。<span><br />\r\n7</span>、 为确保游客合法权益，公司将和游客签定正式旅游合同。<span><br />\r\n8</span>、 如有不详，敬请来电、<span>QQ</span>、<span>MSN</span>垂询。 <span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:ˎ̥;font-size:9pt;">9</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">、接站</span><span style="font-family:ˎ̥;font-size:9pt;">(</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">接机</span><span style="font-family:ˎ̥;font-size:9pt;">)</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">方式：请看手持写有您名字的接站牌，就是我社的安排的接待工作人员，您可以安全的接受她的服务。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 670, '桂林', 3, '大巴', 1, 3, 13, 4, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('Tour', 55, NULL, 1860, '<p>\r\n	象鼻山、刘三姐大观园、七星公园、芦笛岩、尧山、梦幻漓江、靖江王府、印象刘三姐、世外桃源、大榕树、月亮山、古东瀑布、漓江\r\n</p>', '每日', '/attached/image/20120820/20120820103318_126.jpg', '精品纯玩游线路四晚五日游', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">D1<span>、</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">到桂林，接站以后入住酒店，晚上乘船游览<strong>【两江四湖</strong><strong>】</strong></span><span><a href="http://www.guilincyts.com/article/show-sight.asp?id=27"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span></a></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">，座座新桥，景趣相融，各呈异彩，楼亭台榭，错落有致，交相辉映，万盏齐明，灯火阑珊，双塔映月，桥跨银河，宋街连城。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">住：桂林</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">D2<span>、</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">早餐后酒店出发，游览明代朱元璋皇家府邸（靖江王府）<span>90</span><span>分钟</span><span>“</span><span>阅尽皇城知桂林</span><span>”</span><span>，桂林历史文化的变迁，在<strong>【靖江王府】</strong></span></span><span><a href="http://www.guilincyts.com/article/show-sight.asp?id=40"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span></a></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">都&nbsp;可以找到答案。<span>600</span><span>多年历史文化古迹，是明代历史最长，现今保存最完整的潘王府邸。</span><span>“</span><span>桂林山水甲天下</span><span>”</span><span>题词就刻在王城内</span><span>“</span><span>独秀峰</span><span>“</span><span>的石岩上，千山耸立为&nbsp;我独秀的独秀峰，俯瞰桂林全貌，叹古今变迁，日新月异，景景生辉，处处诱人。自助中餐后，游览全国唯一由地下涌泉来形成的多级串连<strong>【古东瀑布</strong><strong>】</strong></span></span><span><a href="http://www.guilincyts.com/article/show-sight.asp?id=86"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span></a></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">，三千多亩的枫树和马尾松，风吹林动，鸟语花香，令人有回归自然的亲切感。</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">住：桂林</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">D3<span>、</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">乘船游览桂林风光之精华<span>—<strong>【漓江】</strong></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span>4</span><span>个小时左右），沿途观看：仙人推磨、鲤鱼挂壁、九马画山、兴坪佳境等景点。让你领略两岸如痴如醉的迷人风光。（船上用自助中餐）船上</span><span>4</span><span>个小时左右游程。中午时分阳朔下船后，酒店休息片刻，酒店休息片刻，前往<strong>【银子岩</strong><strong>】</strong></span></span><span><a href="http://www.guilincyts.com/article/show-sight.asp?id=77"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span></a></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">（游览时间<span>1</span><span>小时）洞内钟乳石高达数十米，方解石微粒的钟乳石在灯光的照射下，照射出银子的光芒。壮族歌仙刘三姐与阿牛哥的定情处，天下情侣圆梦乡</span><span>—<strong>【大榕树</strong><strong>】</strong></span></span><span><a href="http://www.guilincyts.com/article/show-sight.asp?id=54"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span></a></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">（游程<span>60</span><span>分钟）。经过月亮山，坐在车上沿着赏月道，从不同的角度远眺<strong>【月亮山</strong>】</span></span><span><a href="http://www.guilincyts.com/article/show-sight.asp?id=54"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span></a></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">的月洞，移步换景，圆月、半月、眉月的天下奇观，领略人间月亮阴晴圆缺的奇妙变化&nbsp;，晚上<span>20</span><span>：</span><span>00</span><span>观看张艺谋导演的大型山水实景演出<strong>【印象刘三姐</strong><strong>】</strong><strong><u><span style="color:#003399;"></span></u></strong><strong>&nbsp; </strong></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">住：阳朔</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">D4<span>、</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">早餐后，乘车前往</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">国内外专家一致确认，“遇龙河是世界上一流的人类共有的自然遗产。”<strong>【遇龙河</strong><strong>】</strong></span><span><a href="http://www.guilincyts.com/article/show-sight.asp?id=46"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span></a></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:9pt;font-family:''宋体'';">(2人伐）（万景码头——矮山桥）</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">游览时间70分钟，两岸一派田园风光，赏心悦目。让人仿佛进入了天人合一的诗意境界，返朴归真的自由天地。晚上自由漫步闻名中外的“洋人街”-<strong>西街</strong></span><span><a href="http://www.guilincyts.com/article/show-sight.asp?id=50"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span></a></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">；独有的青石板路，观古代民居，灯光下净百家酒吧，酒廊、西餐厅与各国游客交流、对饮其乐无穷。下午返回桂林，自助晚餐后，观神大型表演节目，艺术水准高，极具欣赏价值的<strong>【山水间】</strong></span><span><a href="http://www.guilincyts.com/article/show-sight.asp?id=46"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span></a></span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">(</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">普通票)，观看时间90分钟。</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">住：桂林</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【温馨提示】：</strong>1、以上报价为4-6人报价，人数变动会因为车费的平摊而有所变动，请咨询24小时热线。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2<span>、滑倒或者电瓶车65元/人往返。古东瀑布景区如果游客选择攀爬瀑布游览需 要强制性租用景区内安全设施费用5元</span>/人。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3、免责条款：如遇洪水或其他原因，如旺季和会议包场等原因，不能观看《印象刘三姐》演出的，将按照门票价格退还票款给游客。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4、行程中没有任何强制加点以及强制购物消费项目。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5、本行程为样板，内容可以调整，详情请咨询。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【已含费用</strong>】：<br />\r\n1、【景点门票】行程内所有门票；<br />\r\n2、【漓江船票】漓江（磨盘山——阳朔）；<br />\r\n3、【四晚房费】桂林、阳朔三星标准住宿；\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	4、【导游服务】专职优秀导游讲解；<br />\r\n5、【旅游车费】7座豪华商务旅游车；<br />\r\n6、【保&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 险】旅行社责任险、三十万元旅游平安保险；\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【费用不含】</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n1、团队用餐：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A、单独开餐，游客可根据个人喜好自主决定，自由选择风味特色点菜；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;B、由旅行社或导游推荐安排包餐，标准为早餐5元/人正餐15元/人（10人/桌人数不够份量酌减）；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n2、景区交通：景区内缆车、索道、观光小火车、电梯等代步工具费用；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n3、大交通费：不含游客所在地区往返桂林的机票、火车票等大交通费用；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n4、其他费用：个人的消费、自费项目及因不可抗力因素所产生的额外费用等。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【预订须知</strong>】\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9pt;">1</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">、 请您最迟提前一天向我们预订，旅游旺季及黄金周提前<span>5</span>到<span>10</span>天以上向我们预订<span>(</span>黄金周期间费用上浮<span>100%~200%</span>，请关注本网站变更<span>)</span>。<span><br />\r\n3</span>、 在不减少行程内景点的情况下，我公司有权根据实际情况对行程游览顺序做出相应调整；<span><br />\r\n4</span>、 各种报价标准之间的区别只限于酒店住宿，其他旅游接待服务均相同；<span><span>&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n5</span>、 如遇相关单位价格做出政策性调整则以当时价格为准，恕不另行通知；<span> <br />\r\n6</span>、 游客报名<span>,</span>请将姓名<span>,</span>人数<span>,</span>抵达航班号<span>,</span>车次<span>,</span>时间及联系电话等相关资料通过预定系统<span>,E-mail,</span>电话或传真或网上留言等形式告知我公司<span>,</span>我们将在<span>24</span>小时内与您联系并确认。<span><br />\r\n7</span>、 为确保游客合法权益，公司将和游客签定正式旅游合同。<span><br />\r\n8</span>、 如有不详，敬请来电、<span>QQ</span>、<span>MSN</span>垂询。 <span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;">9</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">、接站</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;">(</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">接机</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;">)</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">方式：请看手持写有您名字的接站牌，就是我社的安排的接待工作人员，您可以安全的接受她的服务。</span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 1860, '桂林', 3, '大巴', 1, 7, 13, 5, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL),
