span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color:#000000;">（不含餐）\r\n住：呼和浩特</span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;"> <br />\r\n</span></span></b>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">上午</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">于桂林机场乘机</span><b><span style="font-size:15.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;"> </span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">MU2330(10:30-12:15)</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">至西安转乘</span><span style="color:#000000;">8L9835(18:10-19:35)</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">或乘</span><span style="color:#000000;">MU2355(21:00-22:30)</span></b><span style="color:#000000;">赴呼和浩特，接机后乘车赴市区，沿途观呼市夜景，入住酒店。</span><span></span></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">第二日：</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">呼和浩特——希拉穆仁草原</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">（</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;color:#000000;">90KM</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">约</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;color:#000000;">1.5</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">小时）</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">（早中晚餐）住：豪华蒙古包</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:blue;"></span></b>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">乘车赴</span><b><u><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">希拉穆仁草原</span></u></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">，</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">抵达草原后，接受蒙古族迎客——</span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;"> </span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">敬献下马酒</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">！体会云淡天地好景 象！骑马（自费）漫游草原，祭拜敖包；访问牧民家庭，亲临蒙古族家庭、品尝牧民自做的蒙古白食——奶制品，午餐品尝民族特色餐——</span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">手扒羊肉</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">，下午观看</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:green;"> </span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#993300;"><span style="color:#000000;">“</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">蒙古男儿三艺</span></b><span style="color:#000000;">”</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">中的赛马及摔跤表演，晚餐后观看民族歌舞表演，参加篝火互动晚会，感受蒙古族的深情与豪放！</span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style="text-align:justify;">\r\n			<b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">第三日：</span></b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;"> </span><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">希拉穆仁草原</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">——成吉思汗</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">（</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;color:#000000;">400KM</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">约</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;color:#000000;">4</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">小时）</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">（早中晚餐）住：</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">鄂尔多斯市达拉特旗</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;"></span></b>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">早起观恢弘的草原日出，早餐后前往伊金霍洛旗，参观一代天骄</span><span style="color:#000000;">——</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">成吉思汗旅游景区</span> </b><span style="color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">【门票</span><span style="color:#000000;">120</span><span style="color:#000000;">元</span><span style="color:#000000;">/</span><span style="color:#000000;">人</span><span style="color:#000000;">(</span><span style="color:#000000;">游览时间约</span><span style="color:#000000;">1.5</span><span style="color:#000000;">小时</span><span style="color:#000000;">)</span></span><span style="color:#000000;">】</span><span style="color:#000000;">，这里以其世界性，历史性，神秘性著称；</span><span style="color:#000000;">带您步入涓涓的历史长河！下午参观内蒙古羊绒生产加工批发基地，这里是内蒙古人自己认可的品牌店——鄂尔多斯</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">都兰迪雅羊绒制品厂。</span></b><span style="color:black;"></span></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">第四日：</span></b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;"> </span><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">成吉思汗——库布齐沙漠</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">（</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;color:#000000;">130KM</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">约</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;color:#000000;">1.5</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">小时）</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">（早中晚餐）</span></b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;"> </span><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:blue;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;">住：呼和浩特</span><span> </span></span></b>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">早餐后，乘车赴中国第六大沙漠</span><span style="color:#000000;">---</span><b><u><span style="color:#000000;">库布齐沙漠</span></u></b><span style="color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">【门票</span><span style="color:#000000;">30</span><span style="color:#000000;">元</span><span style="color:#000000;">/</span><span style="color:#000000;">人】</span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">地处我国文化摇篮</span><span style="color:#000000;">---</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">黄河中游的南缘，库布齐沙漠景观壮美，风光独特。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">车览浊流婉转</span><span style="color:#000000;">的母亲河——</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">黄河</span></b><span style="color:#000000;">。抵达景区后看茫茫大漠、沙丘滚滚，听这里的沙子唱歌，体会西部特有的辽阔；</span><span style="color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">【游览约</span><span style="color:#000000;">1.5</span><span style="color:#000000;">小时】</span></span><span style="color:#000000;">,</span><span style="color:#000000;">也可（自费）参加滑沙、骑骆驼等活动。后乘车返回呼和浩特市。参观具有民族特色、以民族特产、工艺品为主体的</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">蒙亮民族工艺品厂</span></b><span style="color:#000000;">（约</span><span style="color:#000000;">1</span><span style="color:#000000;">小时）</span><span style="color:#000000;">.</span></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;"></span></b>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span></b>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style="margin-left:21.1pt;text-indent:-21.1pt;">\r\n			<b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">第五日：</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:blue;"><span style="color:#000000;">呼和浩特——</span><span><span style="color:#000000;">大召寺——将军衙署——桂林</span><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color:#000000;">（早餐）</span></span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:blue;"></span></b>\r\n		</p>\r\n</span></b><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:blue;">\r\n		<p style="text-align:justify;">\r\n			<span style="font-family:宋体;"><span style="color:#000000;">早餐后</span><span style="color:#000000;">. </span><span style="color:#000000;">市内参观明清时期内蒙古地区最早建立的喇嘛教寺庙也被誉为“银佛寺”的藏传喇嘛召庙</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">——</span><span style="color:#000000;">大召</span></b><span style="color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">（门票</span><span style="color:#000000;">35</span><span style="color:#000000;">元</span><span style="color:#000000;">/</span><span style="color:#000000;">人）</span></span><span style="color:#000000;">(</span><span style="color:#000000;">游览约</span><span style="color:#000000;">30</span><span style="color:#000000;">分钟</span><span style="color:#000000;">)</span><span style="color:#000000;">，后参观</span><b><span style="color:#000000;">将军衙署</span></b><span style="color:black;"><span style="color:#000000;">（门票</span><span style="color:#000000;">25</span><span style="color:#000000;">元</span><span style="color:#000000;">/</span><span style="color:#000000;">人）领略清代一品封疆大吏的威武气势以及武官衙署的建筑风貌，</span></span><span style="color:#000000;">（游览约</span><span style="color:#000000;">30</span><span style="color:#000000;">分钟）</span><b><span style="color:#000000;"> ，</span></b></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">后送机场乘机MU2172（15：15-16:45）至西安转乘CA1225(18:25-20:05)</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;">返回桂林</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#000000;">，结束内蒙古愉快行程!</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n</span></b>\r\n	</p>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;"> </span>', 4150, '桂林', 1, '飞机/大巴', 1, 1, 14, 4, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('Tour', 61, NULL, 330, '大圩古镇、瀑布森林公园、冠岩景区', '每日', '/attached/image/20120821/20120821095659_509.jpg', '古东瀑布、冠岩探险一日游', '<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">早上<span>8</span><span>：</span><span>00——8</span><span>：</span><span>30</span><span>从酒店出发，前往<strong>【大圩古镇</strong><strong>】</strong></span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span style="color:#003399;"></span>参观，之后前往<strong>【古东瀑布景区</strong><strong>】</strong></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span style="color:#003399;"></span>，尽情呼吸清新的空气，感受森林的大氧吧，还有机会和清凉的泉水零距离接触，享受游山玩水的无穷乐趣。&nbsp;下午游览<strong>【冠岩景区</strong><strong>】</strong></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span style="color:#003399;"></span>，体验洞内小火车、小木船、观光电梯等海、陆、空旅游新方式。&nbsp;最后返回桂林，结束愉快行程。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【温馨提示】：</strong>1、以上报价为10人报价，人数变动会因为车费的平摊而有所变动，请咨询24小时热线。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2、免责条款：如遇洪水或其他原因，如旺季和会议包场等原因。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3、行程中没有任何强制加点以及强制购物消费项目。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4、本行程为样板，内容可以调整，详情请咨询。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【费用包含】</strong> <br />\r\n1、门票：大圩古镇、古东瀑布景区、冠岩景区<a href="http://www.guilintravel88.com/article/show-sight.asp?id=56"><span></span></a><span><br />\r\n</span>2、交通：全程空调旅游车&nbsp; <br />\r\n3、导游：优秀导游讲解服务费<br />\r\n4、保险：包含旅行社责任保险\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【费用不含】</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n1、团队用餐：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b