('Tour', 65, 1750, 3530, '<p style="margin-left:68.5pt;text-indent:-68.5pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">★行程特色： 全程 进一个购物店（七彩花市为特色景点不算店），有足够的时间游览景点。<span></span></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">丽江住两晚，让客人有充足的时间感受丽江风光。<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:68.5pt;text-indent:-68.5pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">★景点赠送：世界遗产恐龙王国<span>-</span>禄丰恐龙谷（价值<span>120</span>元）大理苍洱胜景之一崇圣寺三塔<span>(</span>价值<span>121</span>元<span>)</span>、大型实景演出《印象丽江》雪山篇（价值<span>190</span>元）、黑龙潭公园（价值<span>50</span>元）。<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:68.5pt;text-indent:-68.5pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">★特色餐饮：全程中赠送一餐野生菌火锅或过桥米线。每人每天赠送一瓶矿泉水。<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:68.5pt;text-indent:-68.5pt;">\r\n	<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">★贴心服务：导游全程随行陪同，为您做好各地衔接工作，行程作息由导游为您安排，带您感受云南各民族的风土人情。<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">★安全保障：\r\n全程正规输单操作，云南旅游安全组合保险、滇西北安全救助基金让您悠悠玩转彩云之南。</span></b>', '8月25日', '/attached/image/20120821/20120821100435_951.png', '昆明、大理、丽江四星（SPA）双飞6日游', '<div align="center">\r\n	<div align="center">\r\n		<table style="border-collapse:collapse;border:none;" border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n			<tbody>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="52">\r\n						<p style="margin-left:-4.6pt;text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">日期</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="576">\r\n						<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">行<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>程<span></span></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="47">\r\n						<p style="margin-left:-4.6pt;text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">用餐</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="41">\r\n						<p style="margin-left:-4.6pt;text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">住宿</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="52">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:Dotum;color:black;">D1</span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="576">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">乘班机飞往春城</span><span style="font-size:14px;">-</span><span style="font-size:14px;">昆明，鲜花接机，入住酒店。</span></span><b><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="47">\r\n						<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">不含</span><b><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="41">\r\n						<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">昆明</span><b><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="52">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:Dotum;color:black;">D2</span></b><b><span style="font-family:Dotum;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="576">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">早餐后</span><span style="font-size:14px;">BUS</span><span style="font-size:14px;">至大理</span><span style="font-size:14px;">(380</span><span style="font-size:14px;">公里</span><span style="font-size:14px;">,</span><span style="font-size:14px;">行车</span><span style="font-size:14px;">5</span><span style="font-size:14px;">小时</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">途中游览</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">恐龙谷</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;">。</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">)</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">，</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">游览文献名邦</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">【大理古城】</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;">（</span></span><span style="font-family:ˎ̥;color:black;font-size:14px;">40</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">分钟），漫步于中外驰名的外国人旅居的家园</span><span style="font-family:ˎ̥;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">——</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">“</span></b></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">洋人街</span></b><b><span style="font-family:ˎ̥;color:black;font-size:14px;">”</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">，体会独特的异国风情，之后乘车至丽江，</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">晚餐赠送纳西喜宴。</span></b></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="47">\r\n						<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">早中晚</span><b><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="41">\r\n						<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">丽江</span><b><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="52">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:Dotum;color:black;">D3</span></b><b><span style="font-family:Dotum;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="576">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">早餐后，</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">前往具有“东方瑞士”之称的</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">玉龙雪山风景区</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;">（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">120</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟不含排队和上索道时间），乘【</span></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">云杉坪索道</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">】上雪山（含环保观光车），游“高原牧场”</span><span style="font-size:14px;">---</span><span style="font-size:14px;">【</span></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">甘海子，白水河</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">】及被美誉为小九寨的雪山雪融化而成的【</span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">蓝月谷</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">】（</span><span style="font-size:14px;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟，电瓶车自理），东巴圣地【</span></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">玉水寨</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">】（游览时间</span><span style="font-size:14px;">40</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟），玉水寨是纳西族中部东巴圣地，是古城溯源，景区内有众多富有民族、地方特色的景观，如神龙三叠水瀑布群、三文鱼养殖生态观光、古树和玉龙山最</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">大的神泉等景观（游览约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">40</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）。</span></span><span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="font-size:14px;">特别</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">赠送</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;">海拔</span><span style="font-size:14px;">3100</span><span style="font-size:14px;">米，由张艺谋导游的世界最高实景演出</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">《印象丽江》</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;">雪山篇（演出时间</span><span style="font-size:14px;">60</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟），参观</span></span></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">【</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;"><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;">螺旋藻配送中心</span></b></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">】</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">（约</span><span style="font-family:ˎ̥;color:black;font-size:14px;">60</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）游览</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">【</span></b></span><span style="font-size:14px;"><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;">黑龙潭</span></b></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">】</span></b><span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="font-size:14px;">（</span><span style="font-size:14px;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟），</span></span></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">【</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;"><b><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;">大研古城、四方街</span></b></span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">】</span></b><span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="font-size:14px;">（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">90</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）。晚餐自费品尝纳西风味小吃。</span></span></span><span style="color:black;"></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="47">\r\n						<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">早中</span><b><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="41">\r\n						<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">丽江</span><b><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="52">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:Dotum;color:black;">D4<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="576">\r\n						<p style="margin-left:.2pt;text-indent:-.2pt;">\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">早餐后乘车至大理，途中参观新华民族村，</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">游览全国重点文物保护单位，全国优秀旅游城市大理的标志和象征，中国最古老，最雄伟的建筑之一</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">【大理崇圣寺三塔】</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;">（</span></span><span style="font-family:ˎ̥;color:black;font-size:14px;">60</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">分钟，电瓶车自理</span><span style="font-family:ˎ̥;color:black;font-size:14px;">15</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">元），参观大理</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">【大白族民居】</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;">，品尝</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">【三道茶】（</span></b></span><b><span style="font-family:ˎ̥;color:black;font-size:14px;">40</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">分钟），</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;">乘车返回楚雄</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">（行车时间约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">4</span><span style="font-size:14px;">小时）</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">，</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">晚餐赠送特色餐：野生菌火锅。</span></b></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="47">\r\n						<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">早中晚</span><b><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="41">\r\n						<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">楚雄<span></span></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">或<span></span></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">昆明</span><b><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="52">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:Dotum;color:black;">D5</span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="576">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">早餐后</span><span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span style="font-size:14px;">参观地矿珠宝中心并稍作休整（时间</span><span style="font-size:14px;">90</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）</span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">，</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">赴距昆明</span><span style="font-size:14px;">80</span><span style="font-size:14px;">公里的</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">天下第一奇观“石林</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;">”（行车</span><span style="font-size:14px;">90</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟）、游览大小石林（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;">120</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟），观赏那多姿多彩的喀斯特地貌，体味彝族撒尼人的独特风情</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">，</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">游览七彩云南（时间</span><span style="font-size:14px;">160</span><span style="font-size:14px;">分钟，含参观及用餐时间），品云南高原茶艺，聆听茶马古道的历史，了解中国茶文化的起源。</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;">之后</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">下榻</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">超星温泉</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;">。领略露天温泉，</span><span style="font-size:14px;">10</span><span style="font-size:14px;">个温泉泡池让您充分放松休息感受</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">地热温泉养生</span><span style="font-size:14px;">SPA</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;">。温泉水疗</span><span style="font-size:14px;">SPA</span><span style="font-size:14px;">是一种品位、文化、心境等多种元素进行有机组合，从而使您获得一种全方位的生理与心理休闲的超值服务，更是让您得到一种深层次的心理放松、精神愉悦与尊贵感受。在此，您可以完全抛开都市的喧嚣、工作的压力、身心的疲惫而置身于一种心灵深处的安逸与宁静，默默品味一种悠然于世外的境界，真正使人产生回归大自然的全新感受。（请自备泳衣\r\n  露天泡池开放时间：早</span><span style="font-size:14px;">10:00</span><span style="font-size:14px;">～凌晨</span><span style="font-size:14px;">0:00</span><span style="font-size:14px;">）</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="47">\r\n						<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">早中晚</span><b><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="41">\r\n						<p style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">昆明</span><b><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="52">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">D6</span> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" valign="top" width="576">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;">早餐后</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"><span style="font-size:14px;">乘班机返温暖的家，把春城的真诚和美丽带给您的亲朋好友，服务结束！祝您旅途愉快！如返程时间较晚，可自费游览</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">世博园</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;">（</span><span style="font-size:14px;">120</span><span style="font-size:14px;">元</span><span style="font-size:14px;">/</span><span style="font-size:14px;">人含景区内电瓶车）或</span><b><span style="font-size:14px;">云南民族村</span></b><span style="font-size:14px;">（</span><span style="font-size:14px;">120</span><span style="font-size:14px;">元</span><span style="font-size:14px;">/</span><span style="font-size:14px;">人）</span><span></span></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="47">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">早</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;"></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="41">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;">&nbsp;</span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="52">\r\n						<p style="margin-left:-4.6pt;text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">接待</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style="margin-left:-4.6pt;text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">标准</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td colspan="3" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="664">\r\n						<p style="margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;">\r\n							<span style="color:black;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span><span style="color:black;"><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">全程（待评四星）酒店住宿</span><span style="color:black;"> </span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">（因温泉房间偏少入住温泉时间由我社自由安排，但绝对保证客人能入住一晚），</span><span style="color:black;"></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="color:black;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span><span style="color:black;"><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">以上行程所列景点第一大门票及相对游览时间。</span><span style="color:black;"></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="color:black;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span><span style="color:black;"><span>&nbsp; </span>5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">早</span><span style="color:black;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">正，正餐八菜一汤，（十人一桌）</span><span style="color:black;"></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style="margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;">\r\n							<span style="color:black;">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span><span style="color:black;"><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">全程空调旅游车，确保一人一正座。昆明至大理区域交通约</span><span style="color:black;">4~5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">小时、大理至丽江区域交通约</span><span style="color:black;">3~4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">小时。桂林</span><span style="color:black;">-</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">昆明往返机票。</span><span style="color:black;"></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="color:black;">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span><span style="color:black;"><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">优秀地陪导游服务，行程作息由随团导游安排。</span><span style="color:black;"></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="color:black;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span><span style="color:black;"><span> </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">旅行社责任保险。（不含旅游意外保险、玉龙雪山大索道、蓝月谷电瓶车、三塔电瓶车及一切个人消费）</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">。</span><span style="color:black;"></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="color:black;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">行程赠送之景点和项目，如因特殊情况不能安排或客人自愿放弃不游览，费用不予退还。</span><span style="color:black;"></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="color:black;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span><span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">七彩云南、民族村</span></b></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">、</span><span><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">螺旋藻配送中心</span></b></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">为特色参观点，不视同为购物店。</span> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="52">\r\n						<p style="margin-left:-4.6pt;text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">备注</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td colspan="3" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="664">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">此行程不能超过<span>6</span>人在一台车上，<span>6</span>人（连同儿童计算在内）要求在同一部车上<span>+100</span>元<span>/</span>人；<span>7</span>人要求在同一部车上<span>+200/</span>人，<span>8</span>人要求在同一部车上<span>+300/</span>人。学生：<span>13</span>岁<span>-17</span>岁 加<span>600</span>，<span>18</span>岁<span>-26</span>岁加<span>300</span>；\r\n  老年人：<span>53</span>岁<span>-59</span>岁加<span>300</span>，<span>60</span>岁<span>-65</span>岁加<span>600</span>，，<span>65</span>岁以上不予以接待！</span></b><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">为了保证团队质量及便于操作、请严格按照以上行程收客，不要随意更改行程！<b>若遇特殊原因，赠送项目没有产生不退费不换！</b><span></span></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="52">\r\n						<p style="margin-left:-4.6pt;text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">费用</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style="margin-left:-4.6pt;text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">不含</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td colspan="3" style="border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;" width="664">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">1.</span><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">不含自由活动餐费及行程中注明的自理景点费用。<span></span></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">2.</span><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">儿童不含景点门票、床位，产生费用自理。<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">3<span style="background:yellow;">.</span></span><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;background:yellow;">往返机建燃油</span><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">300</span><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">元。<span></span></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style="border:solid windowtext 1.5pt;" width="52">\r\n						<p style="margin-left:-4.6pt;text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">注意</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style="margin-left:-4.6pt;text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n							<b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;">事项</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;"></span></b> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td colspan="3" style="border:solid windowtext 1.5pt;" width="664">\r\n						<p style="margin-left:10.5pt;text-indent:-10.5pt;">\r\n							<span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">1.</span><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">因政治性调价及人力不可抗拒的自然因素以及飞机、火车、轮船本身延误或取消、因交通堵塞或事故及其他各种以外事件等一切非旅行社所能控制的原因造成的团体滞留及所产生的费用由游客自理。<span></span></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">2.</span><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">此团队非纯玩团，旅游地均安排有参观定点购物店，不强制消费，敬请配合参观。<span></span></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style="margin-left:10.5pt;text-indent:-10.5pt;">\r\n							<span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">3.</span><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">我社在不减少旅游景点的情况下有权调整行程，报价为综合价，中间离团门票优惠证件恕不退款。<span></span></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style="margin-left:10.5pt;text-indent:-10.5pt;">\r\n							<span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">4.2-12</span><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">岁、<span>1.2</span><span>米</span><span>以下执行小孩价，</span>小孩含往返机票、半餐费、<span>旅游车位费</span>、导服费、其他费用自理<span></span></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style="margin-left:10.5pt;text-indent:-10.5pt;">\r\n							<span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">5.</span><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:black;">在旅游其间如意见单中未提出异议我社将备案为满意<b>。返程后再提出异议，请谅解我公司不予处理。<span></span></b></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n			</tbody>\r\n		</table>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', 3230, '桂林', 2, '飞机/大巴', 1, 7, 14, 6, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL),
