('Tour', 76, NULL, 700, '漓江（磨盘山-阳朔）、大榕树有、月亮山、印象刘三姐、遇龙河漂流', '每日', '/attached/image/20120821/20120821113301_274.jpg', '漓江风光、阳朔美景、印象刘三姐、遇龙河漂流纯玩二日游', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">D1</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">、早上约<span>8</span><span>：</span><span>30</span><span>我们安排汽车到酒店接您，前往磨盘山码头。登上游船后，您将在接下来约</span><span>4</span><span>小时时间观看<strong>【漓江】</strong></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">全段美景。午餐在船上享用。&nbsp;游船下午<span>14</span><span>：</span><span>00</span><span>左右抵达阳朔。乘旅游车游览<strong>【大榕树</strong><strong>】、【月亮山</strong><strong>】</strong></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">。&nbsp;晚餐后送您前往欣赏国内最精彩的山水实景演出<span>——</span><span><strong>【印象刘三姐</strong><strong>】</strong></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span>。约</span><span>21</span><span>：</span><span>30</span><span>结束表演，我们将送您到酒店。</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>住阳朔</strong></span><span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span><span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">D2、</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">早上<span>8</span><span>：</span><span>00</span><span>出发来到漓江的支流遇龙河上（车程约</span><span>30</span><span>分钟）开始<strong>【遇龙河漂流</strong><strong>】</strong></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">，（游程约<span>1</span><span>小时），观赏河中及两岸景色，两人一片竹筏，泛舟于清澈平缓的遇龙河上体验慢节奏的水上休闲生活。漂流完以后，我们将送您回桂林，并结束愉快的</span><span>2</span><span>日行程。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【费用包含】</strong> <br />\r\n1、门票：漓江（磨盘山-阳朔）、大榕树、月亮山、印象刘三姐、遇龙河漂流<span style="color:#003399;"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	2、住宿：含1晚三星标准住宿，每晚的酒店两人入住一间双人标准间，如出现单房差需补交房费。 <br />\r\n3、交通：全程空调旅游车&nbsp; <br />\r\n4、导游：优秀导游讲解服务费<br />\r\n5、保险：包含旅行社责任保险 <br />\r\n<strong>【费用不含】</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n1、团队用餐：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A、单独开餐，游客可根据个人喜好自主决定，自由选择风味特色点菜；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;B、由旅行社或导游推荐安排包餐，标准为早餐5元/人正餐15元/人（10人/桌人数不够份量酌减）；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n2、景区交通：景区内缆车、索道、观光小火车、电梯等代步工具费用；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n3、大交通费：不含游客所在地区往返桂林的机票、火车票等大交通费用；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n4、其他费用：个人的消费、自费项目及因不可抗力因素所产生的额外费用等。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>【预订须知</strong>】：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:9pt;">1</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">、 请您最迟提前一天向我们预订，旅游旺季及黄金周提前<span>5</span>到<span>10</span>天以上向我们预订<span>(</span>黄金周期间费用上浮<span>100%~200%</span>，请关注本网站变更<span>)</span>。<span><br />\r\n3</span>、 在不减少行程内景点的情况下，我公司有权根据实际情况对行程游览顺序做出相应调整；<span><br />\r\n4</span>、 各种报价标准之间的区别只限于酒店住宿，其他旅游接待服务均相同；<span><span>&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n5</span>、 如遇相关单位价格做出政策性调整则以当时价格为准，恕不另行通知；<span> <br />\r\n6</span>、 游客报名<span>,</span>请将姓名<span>,</span>人数<span>,</span>抵达航班号<span>,</span>车次<span>,</span>时间及联系电话等相关资料通过预定系统<span>,E-mail,</span>电话或传真或网上留言等形式告知我公司<span>,</span>我们将在<span>24</span>小时内与您联系并确认。<span><br />\r\n7</span>、 为确保游客合法权益，公司将和游客签定正式旅游合同。<span><br />\r\n8</span>、 如有不详，敬请来电、<span>QQ</span>、<span>MSN</span>垂询。 <span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;">9</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">、接站</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;">(</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">接机</span><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:ˎ̥;">)</span><span style="font-size:9pt;">方式：请看手持写有您名字的接站牌，就是我社的安排的接待工作人员，您可以安全的接受她的服务。</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 700, '桂林', 1, '大巴', 2, 2, 13, 4, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('DiyTour', 80, 1, 1, '<p align="center">\r\n	<img src="/attached/image/20120907/20120907111459_593.png" alt="" height="389" width="542" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">北京-桂林自驾车地图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	详细路段：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	1、沿G4行驶1225.9公里（经杜家坎收费站，北京南收费站（涿州），临漳收费站（安阳），豫鄂收费站（罗山）），过渔业村约550米后进入京港澳高速。<br />\r\n2、沿京港澳高速行驶74.4公里（经鄂南收费站（赤壁）），过二屋饶家约250米后进入京珠高速/G4<br />\r\n3、沿京珠高速/G4行驶348公里，从衡阳/永州/桂林出口离开，进入衡昆高速/沿衡昆高速一直向前行驶266.7公里，从 兴安/灵渠出口离开，进入G322详细路段/\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	4、沿衡昆高速行驶206.8公里（经枣木铺收费站（永州）），过坝上约250米后进入全兴高速/\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	5、沿全兴高速行驶59.8公里（经兴安收费站），从兴安/灵渠出口离开，进入G322\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n6、沿G322一直向前行驶66公里，过红十字会博爱医院约50米后进入中山中路\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	7、进入桂林市城区\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>', '每日', '/attached/image/20120907/20120907110739_218.png', '【地图】北京至桂林自驾车地图', '', 1, '各地-桂林', 4, 