sp;若遇人力不可抗拒原因或其他因素造成行程变动，我社在不影响服务的情况下有权调整路线，&nbsp;如遇人力不可抗因素造成的团队滞留,所产生的费用客人自理，如出现单男或单女旅行社有权调整三人间或由客人补足房差</span><span style="color:#000000;text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">。</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">2、如遇政府政策性调价差价由客人自理；出团时请带好身份证原件，儿童请带户口本原件，航班、火车时间以航空公司、火车站当天通知为准！！！团队机票为折扣机票，出票后不得签转、退票、换名！中途因客人原因离团，做客人自愿放弃房、餐、景点。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-family:''宋体'';"><span><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 550, '桂林', 1, '大巴', 6, 2, 14, 1, 2, NULL, '涠洲岛是广西最大的海岛，也是我国最大最年轻的火山岛。岛上气候宜人，资源丰富，风光秀丽，景色迷人，四季如春，气候温暖湿润，富含负氧离子的空气清新宜人', '北海 涠洲岛'),
('OverseasTour', 89, NULL, 1680, '<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 越南北与中国广西接壤，西与老挝、柬埔寨交界，东面、南面临南海，一个出境方便的东南亚城市。从没有出过国门的朋友，可以先从越南入手！</span></span>', '每日', '/attached/image/20121029/20121029150232_908.jpg', '越南凭祥三天两晚游（无护照）', '<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029152400_83.jpg" alt="" height="196" width="312" />&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029151308_253.jpg" alt="" height="198" width="302" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第一天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">桂林乘火车K9303前往南宁（16：15发车）抵达南宁。 &nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">住南宁</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>第二天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">早上7点钟乘车前往中国九大名关之一的</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【友谊关】，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">办证处面见办理出境手续</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">中餐后</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">乘车往河内，途中休息参观越南的77土特产店（停留30分钟左右）。车观河内最繁华、最热闹的中心湖——【</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">还剑湖</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">】、游河内旧城的老商业区、被誉为“三十六条古街”的</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">【桃横街】</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">晚上可自由活动或于河内古街感受中西文化交融的殖民古都风情，或于还剑湖边的咖啡厅喝一杯越南中原咖啡</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 住河内</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029151332_504.jpg" alt="" height="198" width="309" /> <img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029151404_840.jpg" alt="" height="197" width="304" /></span> \r\n</p>\r\n</span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><strong>第三天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">早餐后</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">参观越南的心脏---</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">-【巴亭广场】</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">（整个游览约2.5H）</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">主席府</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">胡志明陵</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">，</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">军事博物馆</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">（</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">周一五为保养期，只观外景</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">）、小木屋、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">由一根石柱撑起的</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">独柱寺</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">、最为耀眼的中国驻越南大使馆。</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">乘车</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">前往世界文化遗产—下龙，</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">途中休息参观越南下龙湾免税店（停留30分钟左右）</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">，</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">乘船出海游（约4小时）世界自然遗产八大奇观之一“海上桂林”</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【下龙湾】</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">登岛屿</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">天宫洞、</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">船游</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">狼狗石、香炉山、海上渔村、老人岛、斗鸡石</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">可自费前往越南最浪漫、最漂亮的岛屿一天堂岛（150元/人约120分钟），后</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">下船，告别上帝赐于越南最好的礼物---下龙湾</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">；往酒店办理入住手续。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 住下龙</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><strong>第四天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">早餐后返友谊关入境，中餐后返南宁，结束愉快行程！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>费用包含：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">1、住宿：全程双人标准间；</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;">2、交通：境外段空调旅游车； </span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">3、门票：景点首道门票&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">4、导服：领队和当地中文导游；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">5、用餐：5正2早（境外段正餐标准20元/人、国内段18元/正/标、十人一桌、八菜一汤；早餐为酒店围桌早）；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">6、</span></span></span></span></span><span style="color:#000000;">南宁-凭祥往返交通</span></span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，通行证</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;">。</span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n</span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>费用不含：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">1、桂林—南宁火车硬座65元/人/</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">2、</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">相片制作费20元/人</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">3、一切私人消费（如长话费、洗衣、娱乐等及超行程的费用以及自费项</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">目）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">4、境外段旅游意外险30元/人：保险金额30万元人民币/人</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">温馨提示：</span></strong> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">1、因人力不可抗拒的因素造成的滞留费用由客人自理（如交通事故、自然灾害、社会因素等）。</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">2、患有高血压、心脏等疾病，报名时请作特别说明。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:13.1500pt;text-indent:-15.3300pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">3、行程中产生单男单女，旅行社有权调整夫妻房、三人间或由客人自理单房差。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:13.1500pt;text-indent:-15.3300pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">4、</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">请客人随身携带身份证原件（小孩需携带户口本原件）和三张2寸白底免冠彩照．</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">5、人民币在越南市场流通。越南时间比中国慢一小时，如越南9点，则中国10点。</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">6、凡持有中华人民共和国居民身份证、小孩持户口本均可报名参游（除法律规定不准出境的五种情形、港澳和台湾地区游客外）敏感地区和特殊身份游客按特殊情况申办。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;7、出境前必须按要求填写、提供准确的游客身份资料（通行证申请表、团单表.禁赌保证书、公务员单位证明等）；　组团社需提前两个工作日提供客人身份证复印或扫描件到我社预审查询。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 1680, '桂林', 5, '火车', 5, 3, 2, 2, 2, 3, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tour` (`dtype`, `id`, `children`, `door_price`, `feature`, `group_date`, `image`, `name`, `plan`, `privilege`, `start_city`, `version`, `way`, `address`, `tour_day`, `type`, `sort`, `recommend`, `city_id`, `description`, `keywords`) VALUES
('OverseasTour', 90, NULL, 1280, '<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 越南北与中国广西接壤，西与老挝、柬埔寨交界，东面、南面临南海，一个出境方便的东南亚城市。从没有出过国门的朋友，可以先从越南入手！</span></span>', '每日', '/attached/image/20121029/20121029151404_840.jpg', '越南东兴四天三晚常规游（有护照）', '<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029153359_477.jpg" alt="" height="240" width="316" />&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029153408_269.jpg" alt="" height="240" width="358" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">第一天：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">桂林乘火车前往南宁&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 住南宁</span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第二天：</strong></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早上7：30在铁道饭店或海格拉斯统一集合，乘7：40左右的空调旅游车往中越边境口岸城市东兴市，抵达东兴市后约</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">11</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">点于酒店用中餐和稍事休息【约</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">1-1.5</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">小时】，约</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">12</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">：</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">00</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">分</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">经东兴口岸办手续出境至芒街参观好雅或东盟土特产店</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">（</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">约</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">1-1.5</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">小时</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">）</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，观<strong>北仑河风光，中越友谊大桥，芒街特区风情游</strong>，下约15：00分转</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">乘车【芒街－下龙约</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">180</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">公里，车程约</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">4</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">小时】抵达后入住酒店</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>住下龙</strong></span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029153625_928.jpg" alt="" height="245" width="317" />&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029153646_615.jpg" alt="" height="244" width="339" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">第三天：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早餐后乘越南</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">特色红木</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">游船，倘佯于万顷碧波之中。</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">漫游被国际教科文组织评为世界自然遗产之一的“海上桂林”</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">—</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">【下龙湾</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">】（游览时间约4H）（在1500多平方公里的海面上、耸立着3600多座大小不一、千姿百态的喀斯特地貌的山石、更以其“海美、山幽、洞奇”三绝而享誉天下）、斗鸡岛、狼狗石、香炉山、天宫洞</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">等</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">数不胜数的风景尽收眼底</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">下龙湾亦有小渔船如影相随，可向渔民就地购买些许刚打捞而起的各种鱼、虾、蟹等美味海鲜，让游船厨工加工烹饪。中餐于游船上把酒临风，去国怀乡之忧荡然无存，在天海一色中的游船上大快朵颐的美妙感觉在您的全身悄悄蔓延。午餐后</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">可</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">自费</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">前往越南最浪漫、最漂亮的岛屿一天堂岛（180元/人约120分钟），后</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">下船，告别上帝赐于越南最好的礼物---下龙湾，</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">BUS</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">越南首都河内</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">途中休息参观越南的77土特产店</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">（停留</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">分钟左右）</span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">。</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">沿途可欣赏田园风光等各种异国风景，晚上可自由活动或于河内古街感受中西文化交融的殖民古都风情，或于还剑湖边的咖啡厅喝一杯越南中原咖啡&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong> <br />\r\n</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 住河内</strong></span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029151332_504.jpg" alt="" height="265" width="341" /> <img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029151308_253.jpg" alt="" height="267" width="344" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><strong>第四天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早餐后参观越南的心脏</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">---</span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">-</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">【巴亭广场</span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">】（整个游览约</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">2.5H</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">）</span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">主席府</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">胡志明陵</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">，</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">军事博物馆</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">（</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">周一五为保养期，只观外景</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">）、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">胡志明故居</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">、小木屋、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">由一根石柱撑起的</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">独柱寺</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">、最为耀眼的中国驻越南大使馆。</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">车观河内最繁华、最热闹的中心湖——“【</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">还剑湖</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">】”、游河内旧城的老商业区、被誉为“三十六条古街”的【</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">桃横街】</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">中餐后</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">BUS</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">下龙</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">途中休息参观越南下龙湾免税店</span>（停留30分钟左右） &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp; 住下龙</strong></span>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第五天：&nbsp;</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早餐后BUS下龙乘车赴芒街办理入境手续时参观嘉莉杂货店，入境手续回国，中餐后乘车返南宁，结束愉快行程！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>费用</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>包含：</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">1、住房:下龙越式三；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">2、旅游签证；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">3、景点首道门票；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">4、用餐：7正3早；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">5、交通：空调旅游车；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">6、越南中文导游服务，全程中国导游陪同服务。</span><span style="font-size:10.0000pt;font-family:''新宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.0000pt;font-family:''新宋体'';"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.0000pt;font-family:''新宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>费用不含：</strong></span> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">办理护照，个人旅游意外保险费。超出行程以外和自费项目的费用。属私人消费的费用(长话费、洗衣、娱乐)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:10.0000pt;font-family:''新宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>温馨提示：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.0000pt;font-family:''新宋体'';"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:18.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">1、&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">请提前3个工作日提供清晰的护照复印件给我社，元件和4张白底彩照相片请随身携带。</span><span style="font-size:10.0000pt;font-family:''新宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:18.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">2、&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">越南政府规定胡志明陵每逢周一、五及每天下午不对外开放。</span><span style="font-size:10.0000pt;font-family:''新宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:18.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">3、&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">旅游争议：</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">1</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">）旅行社在不减少行程及景点的条件下，可自行适当调整行程及景点游览顺序，</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">2</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">）若遇人力不可抗拒的因素造成行程滞留或延误所产生的费用客人自理，我社概不负责。</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">3</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">）游客在当地如有不满意之处，请立即告知我社，所有问题在当地处理；为了保证我们的服务质量同时也为了保障旅游者的利益，请您认真填写当地（特别是越南）导游所发的旅游反馈表，一旦出现旅游质量问题，我社将依据反馈表进行裁定！</span><span style="font-size:10.0000pt;font-family:''新宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:18.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">4、&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">台湾的游客须提供多次往返中国大陆签证3个月以上有限期，并在出团时随身携带护照、台胞证和四张白底彩色2寸的相片</span><span style="font-size:10.0000pt;font-family:''新宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:18.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">5、&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">越南的道路上没有公用卫生间，所有的客人只要上洗手间就只能到路边的购物店里上，在购物店买东西跟旅行社无关。</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''新宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.0000pt;font-family:''新宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 1280, '桂林', 2, '火车', 5, 4, 2, 2, 2, 3, NULL, NULL),
('Tour', 91, NULL, 550, '<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 巴马是</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">世界</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">五大长寿之乡中百岁老人分布率最高的地区，被誉为“</span><b><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">世界长寿之乡·中国人瑞圣地</span></b><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">”，也是中国的“<strong>香猪之乡</strong>”</span>', '每日', '/attached/image/20121029/20121029160407_240.jpg', '巴马一地精华二日游A线', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">第一天：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">桂林乘坐</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">K318</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">次火车前往南宁。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 住 火车</span></span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（以上车次为参考车次，准确车次以当时出团实际情况为准）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029160705_514.jpg" alt="" height="199" width="303" />&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029160725_141.jpg" alt="" height="200" width="317" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第二天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">次日早上</span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">05:35分抵达南宁。</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">早上</span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">07:30</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">南宁维也纳酒店（原南方大酒店）门口集合</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">出发</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">往巴马（280公里，车程4小时），</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">中餐</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">后</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">到</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">长寿村</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">-</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">巴盘屯</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">与百岁老人交流长寿秘诀（</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">公里，车程</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">分钟，游览</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">40</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">分钟）后</span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';">前往被英国皇家洞穴协会命名为“天下第一洞”的</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">游览</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">百魔洞</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">（5公里，车程5分钟，游览1.5小时）</span><span style="font-style:italic;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">这里</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">常年祥雾弥漫，经测定此洞中负氧离子浓度高达每平方厘米7万个，是人们进行康复疗养的圣地。洞内有暗洞、奇山、天坑，洞顶居住着瑶民。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">百魔洞内</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">有石英、石柱、石幔、石观音菩萨等，千姿百态、令人目不暇接；后前往</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">参观巴马长寿隧道——盘阳河的穿山岩洞、富含天然负氧离子、百鸟争宿、雄伟多姿的</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">百鸟岩</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">（</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">35</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">公里，</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">35</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">分钟，</span></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">游览1小时</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">）</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">您可以置身如梦幻般地经历六天六夜，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">“时空隧道”的传说足以满足你的好奇心，</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">晚上返回县城入住酒店（</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">公里，</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">分钟），</span></span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">晚餐后自由漫步寿乡文化广场，感受巴马人对生活的热情，让您融入简单而淳朴的快乐气氛中。&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong> 住巴马</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029160855_469.jpg" alt="" height="186" width="314" />&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029160914_24.jpg" alt="" height="185" width="299" /></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>第三天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">早餐</span></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">后</span><span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">可</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">自费</span><span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">乘</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">车前往</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">水晶宫</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">45公里，车程1.5小时，游览1.5小时），在这里你将会惊叹大自然的鬼斧神工：精巧玲珑的石花、晶莹亮丽的钟乳石、雄伟壮观的洞厅构成了大自然精美的科学与艺术的宫殿</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">或</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">自由游览巴马县城，自由选购寿乡特产-长寿食品</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">中餐后返南宁（280公里，车程4小时）,&nbsp;&nbsp;结束愉快的神秘之旅!</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">晚上或下午乘坐火车返回桂林，回到温馨的家</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">费用包含：</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">1、住宿：</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">巴马县城双人标准间；</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（以上报价不含单房差）；</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:0.1000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">2、用餐：</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">全程含1早3正（正餐8菜1汤，10人一桌，人数不足十人，酌量减少）</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">不含酒水；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">3、交通：</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">当地</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">旅游空调车；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">4、门票：</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">百魔洞、巴盘屯、百鸟岩门票；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';color:#000000;">5</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">、保险：旅行社责任险</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">6、导服：当地导游服务；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>费用不含：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">桂林</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">-南宁往返火车车费（130元人）、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">行程外费用及个人消费费用，报价范围外的其他费用</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">，</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">自费项目：水晶宫&nbsp;180元/人</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">、旅游意外伤害保险、</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.1000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;">\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">温馨提示：</span></strong><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.1000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">1、行程中如遇不可抗力因素发生团队滞留而产生的费用由客人自理。我社协调解决。</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">2、友情提醒：在巴盘屯与百岁老人交流长寿秘诀时，请您自备一个零钱小红包，给自己添福给老人添寿。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 550, '桂林', 4, '火车', 9, 2, 14, 2, 2, 5, NULL, NULL);
