('Tour', 92, NULL, 650, '<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 巴马是</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">世界</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">五大长寿之乡中百岁老人分布率最高的地区，被誉为“</span><b><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">世界长寿之乡·中国人瑞圣地</span></b><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">”，也是中国的“<strong>香猪之乡</strong>”</span>', '每日', '/attached/image/20121029/20121029160407_240.jpg', '巴马一地精华二日游B线', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">第一天：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">桂林乘坐</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">K318</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">次火车前往南宁。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 住 火车</span></span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（以上车次为参考车次，准确车次以当时出团实际情况为准）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<img src="http://www.glsits.com/attached/image/20121029/20121029160705_514.jpg" alt="" height="199" width="303" />&nbsp; <img src="http://www.glsits.com/attached/image/20121029/20121029160725_141.jpg" alt="" height="200" width="317" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第二天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">次日早上</span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">05:35分抵达南宁。</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">早上</span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">07:30</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">南宁维也纳酒店（原南方大酒店）门口集合</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">出发</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">往巴马（280公里，车程4小时），</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">中餐</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">后</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">到</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">长寿村</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">-</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">巴盘屯</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">与百岁老人交流长寿秘诀（</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">公里，车程</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">分钟，游览</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">40</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">分钟）后</span></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';">前往被英国皇家洞穴协会命名为“天下第一洞”的</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">游览</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">百魔洞</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">（5公里，车程5分钟，游览1.5小时）</span><span style="font-style:italic;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">这里</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">常年祥雾弥漫，经测定此洞中负氧离子浓度高达每平方厘米7万个，是人们进行康复疗养的圣地。洞内有暗洞、奇山、天坑，洞顶居住着瑶民。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">百魔洞内</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">有石英、石柱、石幔、石观音菩萨等，千姿百态、令人目不暇接；后前往</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">参观巴马长寿隧道——盘阳河的穿山岩洞、富含天然负氧离子、百鸟争宿、雄伟多姿的</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">百鸟岩</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">（</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">35</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">公里，</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">35</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">分钟，</span></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">游览1小时</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">）</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">您可以置身如梦幻般地经历六天六夜，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">“时空隧道”的传说足以满足你的好奇心，</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">晚上返回县城入住酒店（</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">公里，</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">分钟），</span></span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">晚餐后自由漫步寿乡文化广场，感受巴马人对生活的热情，让您融入简单而淳朴的快乐气氛中。&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong> 住巴马</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><img src="http://www.glsits.com/attached/image/20121029/20121029160855_469.jpg" alt="" height="186" width="314" />&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="http://www.glsits.com/attached/image/20121029/20121029160914_24.jpg" alt="" height="185" width="299" /></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>第三天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">早餐</span></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">后</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;"></span><span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">乘</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">车前往</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">水晶宫</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">45公里，车程1.5小时，游览1.5小时），在这里你将会惊叹大自然的鬼斧神工：精巧玲珑的石花、晶莹亮丽的钟乳石、雄伟壮观的洞厅构成了大自然精美的科学与艺术的宫殿</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">或</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">自由游览巴马县城，自由选购寿乡特产-长寿食品</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">中餐后返南宁（280公里，车程4小时）,&nbsp;&nbsp;结束愉快的神秘之旅!</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">晚上或下午乘坐火车返回桂林，回到温馨的家</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">费用包含：</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">1、住宿：</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">巴马县城双人标准间；</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（以上报价不含单房差）；</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:0.1000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">2、用餐：</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">全程含1早3正（正餐8菜1汤，10人一桌，人数不足十人，酌量减少）</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">不含酒水；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">3、交通：</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">当地</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">旅游空调车；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">4、门票：</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">百魔洞、巴盘屯、百鸟岩门票；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''Times New Roman'';color:#000000;">5</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">、保险：旅行社责任险</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">6、导服：当地导游服务；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>费用不含：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">桂林</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">-南宁往返火车车费（130元人）、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">行程外费用及个人消费费用，报价范围外的其他费用</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">、旅游意外伤害保险、</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.1000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;">\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">温馨提示：</span></strong><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:24.1000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">1、行程中如遇不可抗力因素发生团队滞留而产生的费用由客人自理。我社协调解决。</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">2、友情提醒：在巴盘屯与百岁老人交流长寿秘诀时，请您自备一个零钱小红包，给自己添福给老人添寿。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 650, '桂林', 3, '火车', 9, 2, 14, 2, 2, 5, NULL, NULL),
('Tour', 93, NULL, 650, '<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 巴马是</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">世界</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">五大长寿之乡中百岁老人分布率最高的地区，被誉为“</span><b><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">世界长寿之乡·中国人瑞圣地</span></b><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">”，也是中国的“<strong>香猪之乡</strong>”</span>', '每日', '/attached/image/20121030/20121030104921_927.jpg', '长寿巴马凤山精华景点三日游', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第一天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">桂林乘坐</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">K318</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">次火车前往南宁。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 住车上</span></span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（以上车次为参考车次，准确车次以当时出团实际情况为准）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div align="center">\r\n	<img src="/attached/image/20121030/20121030105220_913.jpg" alt="" height="236" width="319" />&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121030/20121030105237_106.jpg" alt="" height="236" width="351" /> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>第二天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 次日早上</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">05:35分抵达南宁。</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早上</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">07:30</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">南宁集中出发往巴马（280公里，车程4小时），中餐后</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">乘车前往</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">长寿之河——盘阳河</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">的源头，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>凤山三门海国家地质公园</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（20公里，车程20分钟，游览1小时），乘船游览世界级天窗（天坑）群，领略大自然鬼斧神工造就的地质奇观，后到</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>长寿村-巴盘屯</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">与百岁老人交流长寿秘诀（30公里，车程30分钟，游览40分钟），后返巴马</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">晚餐后自由漫步寿乡文化广场，感受巴马人对生活的热情，让您融入简单而淳朴的快乐气氛中。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong> 住巴马</strong><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> \r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029160725_141.jpg" alt="" height="246" width="355" />&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029160855_469.jpg" alt="" height="248" width="339" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第三天：</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早餐</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">后</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">前往被英国皇家洞穴协会命名为“天下第一洞”的</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">游览</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>百魔洞</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（5公里，车程5分钟，游览1.5小时）</span><span style="font-style:italic;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">这里</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">常年祥雾弥漫，经测定此洞中负氧离子浓度高达每平方厘米7万个，是人们进行康复疗养的圣地。洞内有暗洞、奇山、天坑，洞顶居住着瑶民。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">百魔洞内</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">有石英、石柱、石幔、石观音菩萨等，千姿百态、令人目不暇接；），中餐后参观巴马长寿隧道——盘阳河的穿山岩洞、富含天然负氧离子、百鸟争宿、雄伟多姿的</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>百鸟岩</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（20公里，25分钟，游览1小时）</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">您可以置身如梦幻般地经历六天六夜，“时空隧道”的传说足以满足你的好奇心，晚餐后入住酒店。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>住巴马</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div align="center">\r\n	<img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029160914_24.jpg" alt="" height="402" width="606" /> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong></strong></span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第四天：</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早餐可</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"><strong>自费</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">前往</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">巴马新开发的超级溶洞---</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">长<strong>寿（水晶）宫</strong></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">（45公里，车程1.5小时，游览1.5小时），在这里你将会惊叹大自然的鬼斧神工：精巧玲珑的石花、晶莹亮丽的钟乳石、雄伟壮观的洞厅构成了大自然精美的科学与艺术的宫殿</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">中餐后</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">返南宁（</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">280公里，车程4小时），结束愉快的寿乡旅程！</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 晚上或下午乘坐火车返回桂林，回到温馨的家。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"><strong>费用包含：</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">1、住宿：巴马县城空调标间；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">2、用餐：全程含2早5正（正餐8菜1汤，10人一桌，如客人不够10人，菜品将按人数减少）；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">3、门票：百魔洞、百鸟岩船票、三门海船票；&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">4、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">导服：全程导游服务；&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">5、用车：</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">当地</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">空调旅游汽车服务</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">1、住宿：巴马县城空调标间；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">2、用餐：全程含2早5正（正餐8菜1汤，10人一桌，如客人不够10人，菜品将按人数减少）；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">3、门票：百魔洞、百鸟岩船票、三门海船票；&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">4、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">导服：全程导游服务；&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">5、用车：</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">当地</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">空调旅游汽车服务</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"><strong>费用不含：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">桂林</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">-南宁往返火车车费（130元/人）、</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">行程外费用及个人消费费用，报价范围外的其他费用</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">，</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">自费景点：水晶宫、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">旅游意外伤害保险</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">温馨提示</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">：</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong></strong><span style="color:#000000;">1、</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">行程中如遇不可抗力因素发生团队滞留而产生的费用由客人自理。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">2、行程中产生单男单女安排三人间或由旅行社调整夫妻房或由客人自理房价差。</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">3、在巴盘屯与百岁老人交流长寿秘诀时，请您自备一个零钱小红包，给自己添福给老人添寿</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:21.0000pt;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 650, '桂林', 2, '火车', 9, 3, 14, 2, 1, NULL, '【凤山三门海国家地质公园】（20公里，车程20分钟，游览1小时），乘船游览世界级天窗（天坑）群，领略大自然鬼斧神工造就的地质奇观', '巴马、凤山'),
('Tour', 94, NULL, 650, '<p style="text-align:justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “东巴凤”，是一个“无山不洞,无洞不奇,山藏幽洞,洞潜碧流,水穿洞出”的世外桃源。这里山青，水秀，洞奇，物美，民淳，人寿!</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="background:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;“东巴凤”&nbsp;，是东兰、巴马、凤山三县的简称，&nbsp;位于广西壮族自治区西部，总面积6133平方公里，总人口70．33万人，其中壮、瑶、毛南族等少数民族人口占总人口85．3%。“东巴凤”是广西农民运动的发源地。是邓小平同志领导的“百色起义”的腹地和右江革命根据地的重要组成部分。70多年前，邓小平、张云逸、韦拔群等老一辈无产阶级革命家曾经在这里运筹和策动了举世闻名的百色起义。</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="background:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">主题活动</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">●&nbsp;访长寿村——由导游带领探访巴马村落，深入了解巴马人的生活习性，寻访巴马长寿的秘诀；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="background:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">行程特色</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">●&nbsp;游览革命老区东兰</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">列宁岩</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">江平田园风光</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">、巴马</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">长寿村、百魔洞、长寿岛、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">凤山</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">三门海天坑群，饱览桂西北淳朴的民俗风情，秀丽的自然风光</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>', '每日', '/attached/image/20121030/20121030110527_37.jpg', '东兰巴马凤山精华四日游', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第一天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">桂林乘坐</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">K318</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">次火车前往南宁。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>住车上</strong></span></span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（以上车次为参考车次，准确车次以当时出团实际情况为准）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong><img src="/attached/image/20121030/20121030112434_297.jpg" alt="" />&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121030/20121030112447_844.jpg" alt="" height="231" width="333" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>第二天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 次日早上</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">05:35分抵达南宁。</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早上</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">07:30</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">南宁集中出发往巴马（280公里，车程4小时），中餐后</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">乘车前往</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">长寿之河——盘阳河</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">的源头，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>凤山三门海国家地质公园</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（20公里，车程20分钟，游览1小时），乘船游览世界级天窗（天坑）群，领略大自然鬼斧神工造就的地质奇观，后到</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>长寿村-巴盘屯</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">与百岁老人交流长寿秘诀（30公里，车程30分钟，游览40分钟），后返巴马</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">，</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">晚餐后自由漫步寿乡文化广场，感受巴马人对生活的热情，让您融入简单而淳朴的快乐气氛中。 </span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp; 住巴马</strong></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong><img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029160725_141.jpg" alt="" height="235" width="339" />&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029160855_469.jpg" alt="" height="234" width="344" /><br />\r\n</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>第三天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早餐</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">后</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">前往被英国皇家洞穴协会命名为“天下第一洞”的</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">游览</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>百魔洞</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（5公里，车程5分钟，游览1.5小时）</span><span style="font-style:italic;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">这里</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">常年祥雾弥漫，经测定此洞中负氧离子浓度高达每平方厘米7万个，是人们进行康复疗养的圣地。洞内有暗洞、奇山、天坑，洞顶居住着瑶民。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">百魔洞内</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">有石英、石柱、石幔、石观音菩萨等，千姿百态、令人目不暇接；），中餐后参观巴马长寿隧道——盘阳河的穿山岩洞、富含天然负氧离子、百鸟争宿、雄伟多姿的</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>【</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>百鸟岩</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（20公里，25分钟，游览1小时）</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">您可以置身如梦幻般地经历六天六夜，“时空隧道”的传说足以满足你的好奇心，晚餐后入住酒店。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>住巴马</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> \r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong><img src="/attached/image/20121029/20121029160914_24.jpg" alt="" height="388" width="586" /></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>第四天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:68.2500pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早餐可</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"><strong>自费</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">前往</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">巴马新开发的超级溶洞---</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"><strong>长寿（水晶）宫</strong></span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">（45公里，车程1.5小时，游览1.5小时），在这里你将会惊叹大自然的鬼斧神工：精巧玲珑的石花、晶莹亮丽的钟乳石、雄伟壮观的洞厅构成了大自然精美的科学与艺术的宫殿</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">中餐后</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">返南宁（</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">280公里，车程4小时），结束愉快的寿乡旅程！</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';">晚上或下午乘坐火车返回桂林，回到温馨的家。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"><strong>费用包含：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">1、住宿：巴马县城空调标间；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">2、用餐：全程含2早5正（正餐8菜1汤，10人一桌，如客人不够10人，菜品将按人数减少）；</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">3、行程内所列景点首道门票</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">4、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">导服：全程导游服务；&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">5、用车：</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">当地</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';">空调旅游汽车服务</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#FF0000;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="color:#FF0000;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<strong><span style="color:#000000;">费用不含：</span></strong></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">桂林</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">-南宁往返火车车费（130元/人）、</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">行程外费用及个人消费费用，报价范围外的其他费用</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">，</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';">旅游意外伤害保险</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<strong></strong><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>温馨提示：</strong></span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">行程中如遇不可抗力因素发生团队滞留而产生的费用由客人自理。</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">行程中产生单男单女安排三人间或由旅行社调整夫妻房或由客人自理房价差。</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:10.5000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">在巴盘屯与百岁老人交流长寿秘诀时，请您自备一个零钱小红包，给自己添福给老人添寿</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 650, '桂林', 2, '火车', 9, 4, 14, 2, 2, NULL, '', '');
INSERT INTO `tour` (`dtype`, `id`, `children`, `door_price`, `feature`, `group_date`, `image`, `name`, `plan`, `privilege`, `start_city`, `version`, `way`, `address`, `tour_day`, `type`, `sort`, `recommend`, `city_id`, `description`, `keywords`) VALUES
('Tour', 95, NULL, 1050, '<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="color:#000000;"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 来这里的人，无不被武陵源奇特的峰林地貌和壮丽的喀斯特景观所倾倒，仿佛置身于仙山仙境之中。</span></span>', '每日', '/attached/image/20121031/20121031101814_816.jpg', '张家界（哈利路亚山）双卧4日游', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第一天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 桂林乘坐专线大巴前往柳州</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 柳州乘坐</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">2012次</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">21:08分</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">或</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">1474次21:46分</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">列车硬卧赴张家界。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">备注：以上车次仅供参考！</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031101814_816.jpg" alt="" height="245" width="327" />&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031101834_989.jpg" alt="" height="243" width="330" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第二天：</strong></span>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早上08：20分抵张家界火车站出口导游写客人名字接，乘BUS前往张家界森林公园<strong>自费</strong>乘坐世界第一梯百龙观光电梯</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>【</strong></span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>百龙天梯</strong></span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>上行56元/人</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>】</strong></span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">加</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>【</strong></span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>土家风情园</strong></span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>120元/人</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>】</strong>加赠送</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>【袁家界景区】</strong></span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">费用</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">共计</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">176元/人导游现收）。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">参观《阿凡达》外景拍摄地&nbsp;“哈利路亚山”即“南天一柱”（又名乾坤柱），探寻阿凡达中的群山漂浮、星罗棋布的玄幻莫测世界；参观云雾飘绕、峰峦叠嶂，气势磅礴的迷魂台、天下第一桥等空中绝景）</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。游</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【天子山景区】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">有峰林之王之称。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">在天子山上观景，视野开阔，气势雄伟，尤其以看峰、观日、赏雾、品雪为绝唱</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">.山下游峡谷两岸林木葱茏,野花飘香;奇峰异石,千姿百态,象一幅巨大的山水画卷的【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">十里画廊景区</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">晚可观看非物质文化遗产基地</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">梦幻张家界表演</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，费用自理：188元/人】，民俗风情演绎，解读大湘西神奇、神秘的巫傩文化。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong><img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031102002_659.jpg" alt="" height="241" width="349" />&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031102043_706.jpg" alt="" height="242" width="346" /></strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第三天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早游览&nbsp;“中国最美丽的大峡谷”</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">金鞭溪景区</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">：神鹰护鞭、文星岩、花果山、金鞭岩、（游览2-3小时左右）千里相会、双龟探溪、水绕四门，张家界国家森林公园,&nbsp;游公园内最大的凌空观景台――黄石寨(约2h&nbsp;)，观摘星台、六奇阁、五指峰、天然壁画等；漫步于“天然氧吧”；后游览土家人心中的圣地国家AAAA级景区—</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">土家风情园</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（游程90分钟）：感受隆重的土家欢迎仪式，欣赏东南第一功、考察摆手堂龙腾柱、土司城堡、土家山寨、九重天土家吊脚楼群、&nbsp;听土家姑娘哭嫁、看茅古斯舞等。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">市区安排25分钟民用大型超市购买生活用品。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">晚</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">上乘坐</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">17：25分2011次</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">或</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">18:46分1473次</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">硬卧返</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">柳州市</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">第四天：</span>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">04:30分返抵柳州。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">散团或乘坐大巴返回桂林。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>费用包含：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong> </strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">★</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">如客人有武陵源大门票优惠按200减优惠价后现退</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">。</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">1、住宿安排：当地</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">经济性或标准型</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">酒店双人标准间或三人间（独卫、彩电、空调、热水）；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">2、用餐安排：1早3正；(正餐15标、早餐6标，团队餐标准)</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">3、交通安排：景区间为空调旅游车；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">4、游览内容：行程中所列景点门票（张家界大门票）&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">5、其它服务：旅行社责任险；</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">6</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">、</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">.当地导游服务（无全陪）；</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">7、小孩只含当地旅游车位和全餐。</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">8、</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">桂林</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">-柳州，柳州-张家界往返大交通</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><br />\r\n<span style="font-weight:normal;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">费用不含：</span> </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">天子山上52元/人、下52元/人；&nbsp;观光电梯单程56元/人；十里画廊小火车往返40元/人、单程30元/人；黄石寨单程50元/人；往返96元/人；凤凰9景148元/人；游客根据整个团队行程时间和自己的爬山体力来决定，不强迫消费；</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">特别提示：</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">散客不提供地接发票（开发票需要收13%的税金）；</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">自费乘坐世界第一梯百龙观光电梯</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">【</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">百龙天梯</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">上行56元/人</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">】</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">加</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">【</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">土家风情园</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">120元/人</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">】加赠送</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">【袁家界景区】</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">费用</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">共计</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:14px;">176元/人）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<strong> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-weight:normal;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n</strong> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>温馨提示：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">1、火车上一切用餐、属于私人消费的费用（长话费、洗衣、娱乐等及超出行程以外的费用）。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">2、儿童不含火车票、景点门票、床位费。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">3、交通票以铁道部门售于旅行社的班次时间为准,出票后不得退票。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">4、如产生单男单女，本社尽量安排三人间、加床、合住，否则请客人现补当地房差。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">5、旅游黄金周及旅游热点时段和地区，如因旅游人数聚增，影响游览时间的，请做好相应的心理准备，并给予充分谅解。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">6、湖南全段酒店均已不提供一次性洗漱用品，请客人自备！</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">7、请携带有效身份证原件，小孩（十六岁以下）带户口本原件 </span><br />\r\n<strong><br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n</strong><br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 1050, '桂林', 5, '大巴，火车', 11, 4, 14, 2, 1, NULL, '    来这里的人，无不被武陵源奇特的峰林地貌和壮丽的喀斯特景观所倾倒，仿佛置身于仙山仙境之中。', '张家界 '),
('Tour', 96, NULL, 1250, '<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color:#000000;">来这里的人，无不被武陵源奇特的峰林地貌和壮丽的喀斯特景观所倾倒，仿佛置身于仙山仙境之中。</span></span></span> <br />', '每日', '/attached/image/20121031/20121031101834_989.jpg', '柳州+张家界（哈利路亚山）凤凰古城 双卧五日游', '<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>第一天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">桂林乘坐专线大巴前往柳州</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">从柳州乘坐</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">2012次</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">21:08分</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">或</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">1474次21:46分</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">列车硬卧赴张家界。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">备注：以上车次仅供参考！</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div align="center">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong><img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031101814_816.jpg" alt="" height="233" width="337" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031101834_989.jpg" alt="" height="232" width="340" /></strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>第二天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早上08：20分抵张家界火车站出口导游写客人名字接，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">武陵源核心景点游</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">自费乘坐世界第一梯百龙观光电梯</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>百龙天梯</strong></span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>上行56元/人</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">加</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>土家风情园</strong></span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>120元/人</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】加赠送</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【<strong>袁家界景区</strong>】</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">费用</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">共计</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">176元/人）。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">参观《阿凡达》外景拍摄地&nbsp;“哈利路亚山”即“南天一柱”（又名乾坤柱），探寻阿凡达中的群山漂浮、星罗棋布的玄幻莫测世界；参观云雾飘绕、峰峦叠嶂，气势磅礴的迷魂台、天下第一桥等空中绝景）。游</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">天子山景区</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】有峰林之王之称。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">在天子山观景，视野开阔，气势雄伟，层次丰富，尤其以看峰、观日、赏雾、品雪为绝唱</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">游峡谷两岸林木葱茏,野花飘香;奇峰异石,千姿百态,象一幅巨大的山水画卷的【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">十里画廊景区</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">晚上可观看非物质文化遗产基地</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">梦幻张家界表演</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，费用自理：188元/人】，民俗风情演绎，解读大湘西神奇、神秘的巫傩文化</span><span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; <br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:9.0000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031102002_659.jpg" alt="" height="242" width="351" />&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031102043_706.jpg" alt="" height="245" width="347" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>第三天：</strong></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早餐后游览&nbsp;【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">中国最美丽的大峡谷--金鞭溪景区</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】：神鹰护鞭、文星岩、花果山、金鞭岩、（游览2-3小时左右）千里相会、双龟探溪、水绕四门，张家界国家森林公园,&nbsp;游公园内最大的凌空观景台――黄石寨(约2h&nbsp;)，观摘星台、六奇阁、五指峰、天然壁画等；漫步于“天然氧吧”；中餐后游览土家人心中的圣地国家AAAA级景区—</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">土家风情园</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（游程90分钟）：感受隆重的土家欢迎仪式，欣赏东南第一功、考察摆手堂龙腾柱、土司城堡、土家山寨、九重天土家吊脚楼群、&nbsp;听土家姑娘哭嫁、看茅古斯舞等。市区安排25分钟民用大型超市购买生活用品。后BUS赴人杰地灵、民族风味浓郁的【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">凤凰古城</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】晚上客人可自由观古城夜景、漫步美丽的沱江放许愿灯，为自己和亲人祈福。途中游览挂在瀑布上的千年古镇---芙蓉镇(自理</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">9</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">0元/人,游览约1.5个小时）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031104135_539.jpg" alt="" height="372" width="553" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>第四天：</strong></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早餐后游览在“沈从文笔下能读到，在黄永玉的画中能看到，在宋祖英歌里能听到”，被新西兰著名作家路易·艾黎称赞为“中国最美的小城”—【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">凤凰古城</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】（古城游览时间约3个小时），</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">漫步明清时代石板小街，细细品味独特的苗疆文化领略苗族风情。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">可选择游览电视剧《血色湘西》拍摄基地—</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">关田山苗寨</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">：一座苗民的风水山，一块一尘不染的净土，自古以来苗民的圣地，</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">中餐后返吉首</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">乘19：33分2011次</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">或</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">20:00分1474次</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">列车硬卧返</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">柳州</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>第五天：</strong></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 04:30分返抵柳州。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">散团或是乘坐专线大巴返回桂林。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>费用包含：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">★</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">如客人有武陵源大门票</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">产生</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">优惠</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">者</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">按200减优惠价后现退，凤凰门票无退费</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">1、住宿安排：当地</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">两晚住房，酒店</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">标准间或三人间（独卫、彩电、空调、定时热水）；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">2、用餐安排：2早5正；(正餐15标、早餐</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">6</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">标，团队餐标准)</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">3、交通安排：&nbsp;景区间为空调旅游车；</span><span style="font-weight:normal;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">桂林</span><span style="font-weight:normal;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">-柳州往返大交通，柳州-张家界，吉首-柳州往返大交通费用。</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:68.2500pt;text-indent:-68.2500pt;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">4、游览内容：行程中所列景点门票；（张家界大门票</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">、</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">）&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">5、其它服务：旅行社责任险；</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">6.</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">、</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">当地导游服务（无全陪）</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>费用不含：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">天子山上52元/人、下52元/人；&nbsp;观光电梯单程56元/人；十里画廊小火车往返40元/人、单程30元/人；黄石寨单程50元/人；往返96元/人；游客根据整个团队行程时间和自己的爬山体力来决定，不强迫消费；</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">特别提示：</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">散客不提供地接发票（开发票需要收13%的税金）</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">自费乘坐世界第一梯百龙观光电梯</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">【</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">百龙天梯</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">上行56元/人</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">】</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">加</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">【</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">土家风情园</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">120元/人</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">】加赠送</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">【袁家界景区】</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">费用</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">共计</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">176元/人）</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>温馨提示：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">1、火车上一切用餐、属于私人消费的费用（长话费、洗衣、娱乐等及超出行程以外的费用）。</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">2、儿童不含火车票、景点门票、床位费。</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">3、交通票以铁道部门售于旅行社的班次时间为准,出票后不得退票。</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:15.7500pt;text-indent:-13.5000pt;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">4、如产生单男单女，本社尽量安排三人间、加床、合住，否则请客人现补当地房差。</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:15.7500pt;text-indent:-13.5000pt;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">5、旅游黄金周及旅游热点时段和地区，如因旅游人数聚增，影响游览时间的，请做好相应的心理准备，并给予充分谅解。</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:15.7500pt;text-indent:-13.5000pt;vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">6、湖南全段酒店均已不提供一次性洗漱用品，请客人自备！</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">7、请携带有效身份证原件，小孩（十六岁以下）带户口本原件。</span><span style="text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 1250, '桂林', 2, '大巴，火车', 11, 7, 1, 2, 1, NULL, '来这里的人，无不被武陵源奇特的峰林地貌和壮丽的喀斯特景观所倾倒，仿佛置身于仙山仙境之中。 ', '张家界 凤凰 武陵源 天子山 桂林旅游 桂林招商国旅 招商国旅 桂林旅游 桂林酒店 桂林旅行社');
INSERT INTO `tour` (`dtype`, `id`, `children`, `door_price`, `feature`, `group_date`, `image`, `name`, `plan`, `privilege`, `start_city`, `version`, `way`, `address`, `tour_day`, `type`, `sort`, `recommend`, `city_id`, `description`, `keywords`) VALUES
('Tour', 97, NULL, 850, '&nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 奔腾东去的沱江水，那柔软的水草，那千年流传的吊脚楼，那醉人的苗家米酒，每一件都是那么清晰的不断闪现，走进凤凰古镇的第一眼，你就会爱上这里。</span>', '每日', '/attached/image/20121031/20121031105930_246.jpg', '神秘湘西凤凰四日游', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第一天：</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 桂林乘坐专线大巴前往柳州</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 从柳州乘坐</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">2012</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">次</span></span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">21:08</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">分</span></span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">或</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">1474</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">次</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">21:46</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">分</span></span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">列车硬卧赴</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">吉首</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">备注：以上车次仅供参考！</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031105837_234.jpg" alt="" height="236" width="335" />&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031105856_256.jpg" alt="" height="235" width="328" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第二天：</strong></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早餐后</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">参观</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">德夯景区</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">沿途可欣赏</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">世界奇观湘西</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">----</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">世界第一悬索</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">大</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">桥。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">这座横跨德夯大峡谷、落差达400米、主跨达1176米的悬索桥，在同类的桥梁中居世界第一。大桥的建成。而当汽车在悬索桥上行走时，那种感觉</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">绝对让人惊心动魄。</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">1.5</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">小时车程</span></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">）</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">游</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">德夯苗寨</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">她是</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">镶嵌</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">在湘西深处的</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">一颗璀璨的明珠——德夯苗族村。“德夯”为苗语，意为美丽的峡谷，距湘西自治州首府吉首市约</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">24</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">千米。这是一块神奇的土地，这里溪流纵横，峡谷深壑，瀑布飞泻，落差达</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">216</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">米的流纱瀑布，如白练凌空，似银纱悬壁。</span></span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">感受苗家待客最高礼仪</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">---</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">拦门酒、卡歌、歌鼓</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">.</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">观苗寨（访村民），对苗歌，观看民俗表演。</span></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">晚餐</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">可自行选择品尝当地小吃，尝一尝血粑鸭、喝一喝苗家酒。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">后自由活动时间，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">可结伴或个人来到中国最浪漫、最灵验的许愿之河</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">"</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">许一个心愿、放一盏河灯、送一份祝福"</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">（购物:刀具店）</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;">晚上客人自由欣赏古城夜景或者</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">自费欣赏天下凤凰篝火晚会或魅力凤凰篝火晚会（约</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">2</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">小时&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">1</span></span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">88</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">元</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">/</span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">人）</span></span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031105930_246.jpg" alt="" height="244" width="362" />&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031110229_718.jpg" alt="" height="215" width="344" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>第三天：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早餐后游</span><span style="font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">美丽的沱江风光、</span><span style="font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">可自费</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">148元/人</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">游</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">一代文豪——沈从文故居、中国第一任内阁总理熊希岭故居，杨家祠堂、梦幻世界——沱江泛舟、北门城楼，明代古桥——虹桥艺术楼、崇德堂、万寿宫、古城博物馆等景点（古城游览约3个小时）</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">】</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">。</span><span style="font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">沱江跳岩、领略好客、纯朴、善良的苗家风情游览古城墙（约1个小时），</span><span style="font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">游</span><span style="font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">沙湾吊脚楼、纯朴、善良的苗家风情游览古城墙（约1个小时），</span><span style="font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">游</span><span style="font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">沙湾吊脚楼、星街北门码头、古城墙、万名塔、参观凤凰古城青石板街、湖南卫视拍摄基地</span><span style="font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">后</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">BUS</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">赴吉首</span></span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''新宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">-----</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">选购湘西特产</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">晚上乘坐</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-family:''Times New Roman'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">17</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">：</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">25</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">分</span></span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-family:''Times New Roman'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">201</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">次</span></span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">或</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">18:46</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">分</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">1473</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">次</span></span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">硬卧返</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">柳州</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''新宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>第四天：</strong></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 次日的早上抵达柳州</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">火车站，</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">散团或从柳州乘坐大巴返回桂林，</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">结束愉快行程。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>费用包含：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">1、住宿安排：当地一晚住房，酒店标准间或三人间（独卫、彩电、空调、定时热水）；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">2、用餐安排：2早2正；(正餐15标、早餐6标，团队餐标准)。</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">3、交通安排： 景区间为空调旅游车。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">4、游览内容：行程中所列景点；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">5、其它服务：旅行社责任险；</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">6、当地导游服务（无全陪）备注：儿童只含半餐和车位。</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">7、桂林-柳州往返大交通，柳州-吉首往返大交通费用</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;"><strong>费用不含：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">魅力凤凰篝火晚会</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">188</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">元/人</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">温馨提示：</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">1</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">、火车上一切用餐、属于私人消费的费用（长话费、洗衣、娱乐等及超出行程以外的费用）。</span></span><span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">2</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">、儿童不含火车票、景点门票、床位费。</span></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">3</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">、交通票以铁道部门售于旅行社的班次时间为准</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">,</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">出票后不得退票。</span></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">4</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">、如产生单男单女，本社尽量安排三人间、加床、合住，否则请客人现补当地房差。</span></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:15.7500pt;text-indent:-15.7500pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">5</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">、旅游黄金周及旅游热点时段和地区，如因旅游人数聚增，影响游览时间的，请做好相应的心理准备，并给予充分谅解。</span></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:15.7500pt;text-indent:-15.7500pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">6</span><span style="color:#000000;font-size:14px;">、湖南全段酒店均已不提供一次性洗漱用品，请客人自备！</span></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="font-family:''华文新魏'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">7、</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">请携带有效身份证原件，小孩（十六岁以下）带户口本原件</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;">。</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;font-size:14px;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 850, '桂林', 3, '大巴，火车', 11, 4, 1, 2, 1, NULL, '奔腾东去的沱江水，那柔软的水草，那千年流传的吊脚楼，那醉人的苗家米酒，每一件都是那么清晰的不断闪现，走进凤凰古镇的第一眼，你就会爱上这里。', '凤凰 德夯苗寨'),
('Tour', 98, NULL, 970, '<span style="color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">奔腾东去的沱江水，那柔软的水草，那千年流传的吊脚楼，那醉人的苗家米酒，每一件都是那么清晰的不断闪现，走进凤凰古镇的第一眼，你就会爱上这里</span></span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">。</span>', '每日', '/attached/image/20121031/20121031104135_539.jpg', '凤凰九景德夯苗寨四日游', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第一天：</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 桂林乘坐专线大巴前往柳州</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 晚上由柳州乘坐</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">2012次</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">21:08分</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">或</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">1474次21:46分</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">列车硬卧赴张家界。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">备注：以上车次仅供参考！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031105930_246.jpg" alt="" height="232" width="349" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031104135_539.jpg" alt="" height="233" width="347" /> <br />\r\n</span>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第二天：</strong></span>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早上06:14分吉首接团，后BUS赴凤凰古城（约1.5小时）欣赏美丽的沱江风光</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">.</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">游【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">南方最美丽的小城——凤凰古城</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">游凤凰古代城墙、苗家吊脚楼、北门码头、北古城楼、沱江跳岩、石板街</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">、</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">虹桥风雨楼、外观黄永玉夺翠楼、万名塔、东正民族商业街、品尝苗家姜糖（游览约4小时）。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">含九景小套票</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">--</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">参观沈从文故居、古城博物馆、熊希龄故居&nbsp;、东门城楼、沱江泛舟、万寿宫、虹桥、杨家祠堂、崇德堂</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。沱江跳岩、领略好客、纯朴、善良的苗家风情，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">游</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">沙湾吊脚楼、星街北门码头</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">、</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">万名塔、参观凤凰古城青石板街、湖南卫视拍摄基地</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">晚餐后自由活动时间，晚上客人自由欣赏古城夜景或者</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">自费欣赏天下凤凰篝火晚会或魅力凤凰篝火晚会（约2小时&nbsp;1</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">88</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">元/人）</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp; <br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031102043_706.jpg" alt="" height="248" width="336" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="/attached/image/20121031/20121031105856_256.jpg" alt="" height="248" width="323" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp; </span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第三天：</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 餐后</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">游【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">德夯景区</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">沿途可欣赏</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">世界奇观湘西</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">----</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">世界第一悬索</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">大</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">桥。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">这座横跨德夯大峡谷、落差达400米、主跨达1176米的悬索桥，在同类的桥梁中居世界第一。大桥的建成。而当汽车在悬索桥上行走时，那种感觉</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">绝对让人惊心动魄。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">（约1.5小时车程</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">）</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">游</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">【</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">德夯苗寨</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">】</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">，</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">她是</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">镶嵌</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">在湘西深处的</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">一颗璀璨的明珠——德夯苗族村。“德夯”为苗语，意为美丽的峡谷，距湘西自治州首府吉首市约24千米。这是一块神奇的土地，这里溪流纵横，峡谷深壑，瀑布飞泻，落差达216米的流纱瀑布，如白练凌空，似银纱悬壁。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">感受苗家待客最高礼仪---拦门酒、卡歌、歌鼓.观苗寨（访村民），对苗歌，观看民俗表演。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">晚餐</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">可自行选择品尝当地小吃，尝一尝血粑鸭、喝一喝苗家酒。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">后BUS赴吉首</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">-----</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">选购湘西特产</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">晚上乘坐</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">17：25分2011次</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">或</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">18:46分1473次</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">硬卧返</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">柳州市</span><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;color:#000000;"><strong>第四天：</strong></span>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 次日的早上抵达柳州</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">火车站，</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">当地散团，或乘坐专线大巴返回桂林。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>费用包含：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">1、住宿安排：当地准一晚住房，酒店标准间或三人间（独卫、彩电、空调、定时热水）；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;">2、用餐安排：2早2正；(正餐15标、早餐6标，团队餐标准)</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;">3、交通安排： 景区间为空调旅游车。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;">4、游览内容：行程中所列景点门票；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;">5、其它服务：旅行社责任险；</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;">6、当地导游服务（无全陪）&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;">7、桂林-柳州-桂林往返专线大巴，柳州-张家界，吉首-柳州往返火车费用</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>费用不含：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">魅力凤凰篝火晚会</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">188</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">元/人</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><strong>温馨提示：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">1、火车上一切用餐、属于私人消费的费用（长话费、洗衣、娱乐等及超出行程以外的费用）。</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">2、儿童不含火车票、景点门票、床位费。</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">3、交通票以铁道部门售于旅行社的班次时间为准,出票后不得退票。</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">4、如产生单男单女，本社尽量安排三人间、加床、合住，否则请客人现补当地房差。</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:15.7500pt;text-indent:-15.7500pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">5、旅游黄金周及旅游热点时段和地区，如因旅游人数聚增，影响游览时间的，请做好相应的心理准备，并给予充分谅解。</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:15.7500pt;text-indent:-15.7500pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;">6</span><span style="color:#000000;">、湖南全段酒店均已不提供一次性洗漱用品，请客人自备！</span></span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"></span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''华文新魏'';color:#000000;">7、</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">请携带有效身份证原件，小孩（十六岁以下）带户口本原件</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;">。</span><span style="font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:''宋体'';"><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;font-family:''宋体'';color:#000000;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 970, '桂林', 1, '大巴，火车', 11, 4, 1, 2, 1, NULL, '奔腾东去的沱江水，那柔软的水草，那千年流传的吊脚楼，那醉人的苗家米酒，每一件都是那么清晰的不断闪现，走进凤凰古镇的第一眼，你就会爱上这里。', '凤凰 德夯苗寨  沈从文故居、古城博物馆、熊希龄故居 、东门城楼、沱江泛舟、万寿宫、虹桥、杨家祠堂、崇德堂');
